# <a name="sensitive-information-type-entity-definitions"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-104">Определения типов конфиденциальной информации</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-104">Sensitive information type entity definitions</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-105">Защита от потери данных (DLP) в центре соответствия требованиям включает множество типов конфиденциальной информации, готовых к использованию в политиках защиты от потери данных.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-105">Data loss prevention (DLP) in the Compliance Center includes many sensitive information types that are ready for you to use in your DLP policies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-106">В этой статье перечислены все эти типы конфиденциальной информации и показано, каким именно образом политика защиты от потери данных выявляет каждый тип.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-106">This topic lists all of these sensitive information types and shows what a DLP policy looks for when it detects each type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-107">Тип конфиденциальной информации определяется шаблоном, который можно идентифицировать регулярным выражением или функцией.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-107">A sensitive information type is defined by a pattern that can be identified by a regular expression or a function.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-108">Кроме того, для идентификации типа конфиденциальной информации могут использоваться подкрепляющие доказательства, такие как ключевые слова и контрольные суммы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-108">In addition, corroborative evidence such as keywords and checksums can be used to identify a sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-109">Уровень вероятности и расположение слов и знаков также используются в процессе оценки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-109">Confidence level and proximity are also used in the evaluation process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-110">Для типов конфиденциальной информации требуется одна из следующих подписок:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-110">Sensitive information types require one of these subscriptions:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span></span>

## <a name="aba-routing-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-113">Номер маршрутизации код банка ABA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-113">ABA routing number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-114">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-114">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-115">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-115">nine digits which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-116">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-116">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-117">Форматируемые</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-117">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-118">четыре цифры, начинающиеся с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-118">four digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-119">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-119">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-120">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-120">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-121">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-121">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-122">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-122">a digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-123">Неформатированный: девять последовательных цифр, начиная с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-123">Unformatted: nine consecutive digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span> 

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-124">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-124">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-125">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-125">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-126">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-126">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-127">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-127">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-128">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-128">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-129">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ABA_Routing.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-129">A keyword from Keyword_ABA_Routing is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-130">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-130">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-131">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-131">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- ABA Routing Number -->
    <Entity id="cb353f78-2b72-4c3c-8827-92ebe4f69fdf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ABA_Routing" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-140">американбанкассоЦиатионраутингнумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-140">americanbankassociationroutingnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-141">банкраутинг #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-141">bankrouting#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-142">банкраутингнумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-142">bankroutingnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-143">включен #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-143">routing #</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-145">номер маршрутизации</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-145">routing number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-146">routing transit number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-146">routing transit number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-147">включен #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-147">routing#</span></span>

## <a name="argentina-national-identity-dni-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-149">Внутренний идентификационный номер (DNI), Аргентина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-149">Argentina national identity (DNI) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-150">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-150">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-151">Восемь цифр с периодами или без них</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-151">Eight digits with or without periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-152">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-152">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-153">Восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-153">Eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-154">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-154">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-155">Необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-155">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-156">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-156">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-157">Необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-157">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-158">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-158">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-159">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-159">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-160">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-160">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-161">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-161">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-162">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-162">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-163">регулярное выражение Regex_argentina_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-163">The regular expression Regex_argentina_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-164">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_argentina_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-164">A keyword from Keyword_argentina_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Argentina National Identity (DNI) Number -->
<Entity id="eefbb00e-8282-433c-8620-8f1da3bffdb2" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_argentina_national_id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_argentina_national_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-165">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-165">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_argentina_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-166">Keyword_argentina_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-166">Keyword_argentina_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-169">кéдула</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-169">cédula</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-170">DNI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-170">dni</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-171">документо наЦионал де ИДЕНТИДАД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-171">documento nacional de identidad</span></span>

## <a name="australia-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-176">Номер банковского счета для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-176">Australia bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-177">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-177">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-178">от шести до десяти цифр со номером филиала банка или без него</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-178">six to ten digits with or without a bank state branch number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-179">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-179">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-180">Номер счета — от шести до десяти цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-180">Account number is six to ten digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-181">Номер филиала государственного банка Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-181">Australia bank state branch number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-182">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-182">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-183">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-183">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-184">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-184">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-185">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-185">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-186">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-186">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-187">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-187">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-188">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-188">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-189">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-189">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-190">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-190">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-191">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-191">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-192">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-192">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-193">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-193">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-194">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-194">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="74a54de9-2a30-4aa0-a8aa-3d9327fc07c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb" />
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
  </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-business-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-210">Бизнес-номер Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-210">Australia business number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-211">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-211">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-212">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-212">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-213">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-213">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-214">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-214">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-215">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-215">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-216">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-216">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-217">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-217">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-218">11 цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-218">11 digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-219">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-219">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-220">11 цифр с необязательными ограничителями:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-220">11 digits with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-221">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-221">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-222">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-222">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-223">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-223">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-224">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-224">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-225">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-225">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-226">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-226">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-227">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-227">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-228">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-228">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-229">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-229">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-230">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-230">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-231">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-231">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-232">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-232">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-233">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_australian_business_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-233">A keyword from Keywords_australian_business_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-234">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-234">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-235">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-235">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Business Number -->
      <Entity id="76e83b3b-01ee-4530-aced-e667a6609f49" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-246">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-246">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-247">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-247">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-248">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-248">communication compliance policies</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-250">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-250">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-251">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-251">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-252">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-252">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-253">девять цифр с разделителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-253">nine digits with delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-254">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-254">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-255">девять цифр с разделителями:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-255">nine digits with delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-256">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-256">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-257">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-257">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-258">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-258">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-259">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-259">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-260">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-260">three digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-261">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-261">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-262">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-262">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-263">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-263">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-264">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-264">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-265">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-265">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-266">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Australian_Company_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-266">A keyword from Keyword_Australian_Company_Number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-267">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-267">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-268">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-268">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Company Number -->
      <Entity id="b1fba4f7-7b3e-4bb9-8f9a-9366df604dbb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_australia_company_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-270">Keyword_australia_company_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-270">Keyword_australia_company_number</span></span>

## <a name="australia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-278">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-278">Australia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-279">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-279">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-280">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-280">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-281">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-281">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-282">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-282">nine letters and digits:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-283">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-283">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-284">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-284">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-285">пять цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-285">five digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-286">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-286">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-287">один-два необязательных буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-287">one to two optional letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-288">от четырех до девяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-288">four to nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-289">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-289">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-290">девять цифр или букв (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-290">nine digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-291">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-291">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-292">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-292">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-293">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-293">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-294">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-294">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-295">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-295">The regular expression Regex_australia_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-296">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-296">A keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-297">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-297">No keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Drivers License Number -->
<Entity id="1cbbc8f5-9216-4392-9eb5-5ac2298d1356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-medical-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-397">Номер медицинской учетной записи Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-397">Australia medical account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-398">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-398">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-399">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-399">10-11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-400">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-400">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-401">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-401">10-11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-402">Первая цифра находится в диапазоне 2-6</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-402">first digit is in the range 2-6</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-403">девятая цифра — это контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-403">ninth digit is a check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-404">Десятая цифра — это цифра, связанная с вопросом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-404">tenth digit is the issue digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-405">Одиннадцатая цифра (необязательно) — индивидуальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-405">eleventh digit (optional) is the individual number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-406">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-406">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-407">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-407">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-408">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-408">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-409">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-409">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-410">функция Func_australian_medical_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-410">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-411">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-411">A keyword from Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-412">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-412">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
  <!-- Australia Medical Account Number -->
<Entity id="104a99a0-3d3b-4542-a40d-ab0b9e1efe63" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-424">Номер паспорта для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-424">Australia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-425">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-425">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-426">Буква, за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-426">A letter followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-427">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-427">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-428">Буква (без учета регистра), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-428">A letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-429">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-429">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-430">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-430">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-431">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-431">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-432">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-432">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-433">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-433">The regular expression Regex_australia_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-434">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_passport или Keyword_australia_passport_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-434">A keyword from Keyword_passport or Keyword_australia_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Passport Number -->
<Entity id="29869db6-602d-4853-ab93-3484f905df50" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_passport_number" />
        </Any>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>   
```

## <a name="australia-tax-file-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-468">Номер файла налога для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-468">Australia tax file number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-469">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-469">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-470">от восьми до девяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-470">eight to nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-471">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-471">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-472">от восьми до девяти цифр, как правило, представляются пробелы следующим образом:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-472">eight to nine digits typically presented with spaces as follows:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-473">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-473">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-474">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-474">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-475">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-475">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-476">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-476">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-477">две и три цифры, где последняя цифра — проверочная.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-477">two to three digits where the last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-478">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-478">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-479">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-479">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-480">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-480">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-481">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-481">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-482">функция Func_australian_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-482">The function Func_australian_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-483">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number или Keyword_number_exclusions не найдено;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-483">No keyword from Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number or Keyword_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-484">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-484">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
   <!-- Australia Tax File Number -->
    <Entity id="e29bc95f-ff70-4a37-aa01-04d17360a4c5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_tax_file_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-496">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-496">Austria driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-497">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-497">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-498">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-498">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-499">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-499">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-500">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-500">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-501">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-501">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-502">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-502">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-503">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-503">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-504">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-504">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-505">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-505">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-506">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-506">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-507">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-507">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="682f18ce-44eb-482b-8198-2bcb96a0761e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-634">Австрийская идентификационная карточка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-634">Austria identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-635">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-635">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-636">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-636">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-637">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-637">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-638">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-638">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-639">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-639">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-640">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-640">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-641">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-641">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-642">24 – символическое сочетание букв, цифр и специальных символов;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-642">A 24-character combination of letters, digits, and special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-643">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-643">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-644">24 символа:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-644">24 characters:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-645">22 буквы (без учета регистра), цифры, обратные косые черты, косые черты и знаки плюса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-645">22 letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, or plus signs</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-646">две буквы (без учета регистра), цифры, обратные косые черты, знаки косой черты, знаки плюса и знаки равенства.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-646">two letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, plus signs, or equal signs</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-647">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-647">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-648">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-648">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-649">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-649">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-650">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-650">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-651">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-651">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-652">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-652">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
   
```xml
      <!-- Austria Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="5ec06c3b-007e-4820-8343-7ff73b889735" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-658">Номер паспорта для Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-658">Austria passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-659">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе сенситивеинформатион Passport Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-659">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitiveinformation type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-660">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-660">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-661">Одна буква, за которой следует необязательный пробел и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-661">One letter followed by an optional space and seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-662">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-662">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-663">Сочетание одной буквы, семи цифр и одного пробела:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-663">A combination of one letter, seven digits, and one space:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-664">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-664">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-665">один пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-665">one space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-666">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-666">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-667">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-667">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-668">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-668">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-669">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-669">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-670">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-670">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-671">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-671">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-672">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-672">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-693">Австрийский номер социального страхования или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-693">Austria social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-694">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-694">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-695">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-695">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-696">10 цифр в указанном формате</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-696">10 digits in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-697">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-697">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-698">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-698">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-699">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-699">three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-700">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-700">one check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-701">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММГГ —)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-701">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-702">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-702">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-703">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-703">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-704">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-704">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-705">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-705">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-706">Функция "Func_austria_eu_</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-706">The function  \`Func_austria_eu_</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-707">_or_equivalent ' находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-707">_or_equivalent\` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-708">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-708">a keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-709">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-709">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-710">Функция  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-710">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-723">созиалверсичерунгснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-723">sozialversicherungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-724">созиале сичерхеит Кеин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-724">soziale sicherheit kein</span></span>

## <a name="austria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-726">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-726">Austria tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-727">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-727">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-728">девять цифр с необязательным дефисом и косой чертой.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-728">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-729">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-729">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-730">девять цифр с необязательным дефисом и косой чертой.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-730">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-731">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-731">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-732">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-732">a hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-733">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-733">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-734">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-734">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-735">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-735">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-736">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-736">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-737">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-737">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-738">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-738">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-739">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-739">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-740">Функция  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-740">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-741">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-741">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-742">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-742">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-743">Функция  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-743">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="4fd58d22-af28-4451-b18a-6f722430a56d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-744">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-744">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-745">Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-745">Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-746">öстерреич</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-746">österreich</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-747">st.nr.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-747">st.nr.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-748">стеуернуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-748">steuernummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-749">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-749">tax id</span></span>

## <a name="austria-value-added-tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-766">Налог на добавленную стоимость (Австрия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-766">Austria value added tax</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-767">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-767">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-768">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-768">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-769">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-769">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-770">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-770">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-771">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-771">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-772">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-772">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-773">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-773">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-774">11-буквенно-буквенно-буквенный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-774">11-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-775">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-775">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-776">11-буквенно-цифровой буквенно-значный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-776">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-777">A или a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-777">A or a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-778">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-778">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-779">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-779">Optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-780">U или u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-780">U or u</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-781">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-781">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-782">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-782">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-783">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-783">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-784">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-784">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-785">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-785">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-786">одна или две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-786">one or two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-787">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-787">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-788">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-788">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-789">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-789">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-790">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-790">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-791">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-791">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-792">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-792">A keyword from Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-793">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-793">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-794">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-794">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="b6a3eda2-c56c-4b69-a5f7-dca34db00f48" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-800">НДС номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-800">vat no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-801">ватно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-801">vatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-802">Налоговый номер добавленной стоимости</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-802">value added tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-803">Австрийский НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-803">austrian vat</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-804">мвст</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-804">mwst</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-807">уст. идентификатионснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-807">ust.-identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-808">умсатзстеуер — идентификатионснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-808">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-809">идентификационный номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-809">vat identification number</span></span>

## <a name="azure-documentdb-auth-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-812">Ключ проверки подлинности Azure DocumentDB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-812">Azure DocumentDB auth key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-813">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-813">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-814">Строка "DocumentDb", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-814">The string "DocumentDb" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-815">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-815">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-816">Строка "DocumentDb"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-816">The string "DocumentDb"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-817">Любая комбинация из 3-200 прописных или строчных букв, цифр, символов, специальных символов и пробелов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-817">Any combination of between 3-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-818">Символ "больше" (>), знак равенства (=), кавычки (") или апостроф (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-818">A greater than symbol (>), an equal sign (=), a quotation mark ("), or an apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-819">Любая комбинация 86 строчных или прописных букв, цифр, символов косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-819">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-820">Два знака равенства (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-820">Two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-821">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-821">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-822">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-822">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-823">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-823">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-824">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-824">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-825">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-825">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-826">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не **находит содержимое** , которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-826">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Azure Document DB Auth Key -->
<Entity id="0f587d92-eb28-44a9-bd1c-90f2892b47aa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
          </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-827">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-827">Keywords</span></span>

Azure".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-843">The string "Server", "server", or "data source" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-844">com "или" клаудапп. ### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-847">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-847">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-848">строка "Server", "Server" или "Data Source"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-848">the string "Server", "server", or "data source"</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-852">Любая комбинация из 1-200 прописных или строчных букв, цифр, символов, специальных символов и пробелов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-852">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-853">Строка "клаудапп. ### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-866">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-866">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-867">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-867">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-868">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-868">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-869">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не **находит содержимое** , которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-869">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IAAS Database Connection String and Azure SQL Connection String-->
<Entity id="ce1a126d-186f-4700-8c0c-486157b953fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-iot-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-884">Строка подключения Azure IoT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-884">Azure IoT connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-885">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-885">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-886">Строка "HostName", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне, включая строки "Azure — Devices.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-886">The string "HostName" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-887">NET "и" Шаредакцесскэй ".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-887">net" and "SharedAccessKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-888">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-888">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-889">строка "HostName"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-889">the string "HostName"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-890">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-890">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-891">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-891">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-892">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-892">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-893">Любая комбинация из 1-200 прописных или строчных букв, цифр, символов, специальных символов и пробелов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-893">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-894">строка "Azure — Devices.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-894">the string "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-895">команде</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-895">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-896">Любая комбинация из 1-200 прописных или строчных букв, цифр, символов, специальных символов и пробелов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-896">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-897">строка "Шаредакцесскэй"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-897">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-898">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-898">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-899">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-899">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-900">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-900">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-901">Любая комбинация 43 строчных или прописных букв, цифр, символов косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-901">any combination of 43 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-902">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-902">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-903">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-903">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-904">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-904">No</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-906">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-906">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
