## <a name="denmark-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3418">Номер паспорта для Дании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3418">Denmark passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3419">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3419">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3420">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3420">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3421">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3421">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3422">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3422">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3423">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3423">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3424">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3424">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3425">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3425">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3426">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3426">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3427">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3427">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3428">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3428">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3429">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3429">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3446">Личный идентификационный номер для Дании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3446">Denmark personal identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3447">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3447">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3448">десять цифр, содержащие дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3448">ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3449">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3449">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3450">десять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3450">ten digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3451">шесть цифр в формате ддммгг — Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3451">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3452">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3452">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3453">четыре цифры, где последняя цифра является контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3453">four digits where the final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3454">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3454">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3455">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3455">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3456">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3456">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3457">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3457">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3458">Регулярное выражение Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3458">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3459">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_denmark_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3459">A keyword from Keyword_denmark_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3460">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3460">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3461">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3461">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3462">Регулярное выражение Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3462">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3463">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3463">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="6c4f2fef-56e1-4c00-8093-88d7a01cf460" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_denmark_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3535">Номер социального страхования для Дании или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3535">Denmark social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3536">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только для номера социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3536">This sensitive information type entity is only available the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3537">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3537">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3538">десять цифр и дефис в заданном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3538">ten digits and a hyphen in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3539">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3539">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3540">десять цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3540">ten digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3541">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММГГ —)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3541">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3542">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3542">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3543">четыре цифры, которые соответствуют порядковому номеру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3543">four digits that correspond to a sequence number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3544">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3544">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3545">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3545">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3546">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3546">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3547">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3547">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3548">Функция  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3548">The function  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3549">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3549">A keyword from  `Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3550">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3550">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3551">Функция  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3551">The function  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="drug-enforcement-agency-dea-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3565">Номер агентства для применения наркотиков (DEA)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3565">Drug Enforcement Agency (DEA) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3566">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3566">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3567">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3567">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3568">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3568">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3569">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3569">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3570">одна буква (без учета регистра) из этого набора возможных букв: abcdefghjklmnprstux, который является кодом Регистрант</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3570">one letter (not case sensitive) from this set of possible letters: abcdefghjklmnprstux, which is a registrant code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3571">одна буква (без учета регистра), представляющая собой первую букву фамилии Регистрант или цифры 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3571">one letter (not case sensitive), which is the first letter of the registrant's last name or digit '9'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3572">семь цифр, последняя из которых — контрольная цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3572">seven digits, the last of which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3573">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3573">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3574">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3574">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3575">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3575">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3576">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3576">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3577">функция Func_dea_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3577">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3578">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keyword_dea_number`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3578">A keyword from `Keyword_dea_number` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3579">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3579">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3580">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3580">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3581">функция Func_dea_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3581">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3582">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3582">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- DEA Number -->
    <Entity id="9a5445ad-406e-43eb-8bd7-cac17ab6d0e4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
      </Pattern>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.1207.000" maxEngineVersion="15.20.3134.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3135.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3583">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3583">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_dea_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3584">Keyword_dea_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3584">Keyword_dea_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3585">DEA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3585">dea</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3586">DEA #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3586">dea#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3587">Администрирование принудительного использования лекарства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3587">drug enforcement administration</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3588">Агентство по принужденным лекарствам</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3588">drug enforcement agency</span></span>


## <a name="estonia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3589">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Эстонии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3589">Estonia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3590">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3590">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3591">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3591">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3592">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3592">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3593">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3593">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3594">две буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3594">two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3595">буквы "ET" (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3595">the letters "ET" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3596">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3596">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3597">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3597">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3598">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3598">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3599">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3599">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3600">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3600">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3601">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3601">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3602">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3602">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="51da8171-da70-4cc1-9d65-055a59ca4f83" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-personal-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3728">Эстонии персональный идентификационный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3728">Estonia Personal Identification Code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3729">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3729">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3730">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3730">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3731">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3731">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3732">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3732">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3733">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3733">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3734">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3734">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3735">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3735">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3736">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3736">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3737">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3737">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3738">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3738">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3739">одна цифра, соответствующая упоминанию секса и столетию рождения (нечетный номер, четная розетка), 1-2:19 века; 3-4:20 века; 5-6:21 столетие)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3739">one digit that corresponds to sex and century of birth (odd number male, even number female; 1-2: 19th century; 3-4: 20th century; 5-6: 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3740">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3740">six digits that correspond to date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3741">три цифры, которые соответствуют порядковому номеру, разделенному на одну и ту же дату.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3741">three digits that correspond to a serial number separating persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3742">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3742">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3743">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3743">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3744">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3744">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3745">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3745">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3746">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3746">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3747">Функция  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3747">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3748">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3748">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3749">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3749">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3750">Функция  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3750">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Personal Identification Code -->
      <Entity id="bfb26de6-dad5-4d48-ab72-4789cdd0654c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3783">Номер паспорта для Эстонии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3783">Estonia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3784">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3784">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3785">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3785">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3786">одна буква, за которой следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3786">one letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3787">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3787">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3788">одна буква, за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3788">one letter followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3789">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3789">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3790">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3790">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3791">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3791">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3792">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3792">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3793">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3793">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3794">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3794">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="eu-debit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3809">Номер дебетовой карты ЕС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3809">EU debit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3810">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3810">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3811">16 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3811">16 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3812">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3812">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3813">Очень сложный и надежный шаблон.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3813">Very complex and robust pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3814">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3814">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3815">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3815">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3816">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3816">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3817">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3817">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3818">Функция Func_eu_debit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3818">The function Func_eu_debit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3819">Верно по меньшей мере одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3819">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3820">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_eu_debit_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3820">A keyword from Keyword_eu_debit_card is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3821">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3821">A keyword from Keyword_card_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3822">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_security_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3822">A keyword from Keyword_card_security_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3823">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3823">A keyword from Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3824">функция Func_expiration_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3824">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-3825">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-3825">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- EU Debit Card Number -->
    <Entity id="0e9b3178-9678-47dd-a509-37222ca96b42" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_eu_debit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_eu_debit_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_security_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4271">Номер водительского удостоверения для Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4271">Finland driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4272">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4272">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4273">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4273">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4274">десять цифр и букв, содержащих дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4274">ten digits and letters containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4275">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4275">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4276">десять цифр и букв, содержащих дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4276">ten digits and letters containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4277">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4277">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4278">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4278">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4279">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4279">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4280">цифра или буква;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4280">a digit or letter</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4281">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4281">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4282">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4282">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4283">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4283">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4284">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4284">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4285">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4285">The regular expression  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4286">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4286">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Finland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="bb3b27a3-79bd-4ac4-81a7-f9fca3c7d1a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-european-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4417">Номер страховки для Финляндии (Европейский)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4417">Finland european health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4418">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4418">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4419">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4419">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4420">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4420">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4421">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4421">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4422">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4422">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4423">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4423">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4424">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4424">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4425">20 цифр номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4425">20 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4426">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4426">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4427">20 – значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4427">20-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4428">десять цифр — 8024680246</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4428">ten digits - 8024680246</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4429">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4429">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4430">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4430">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4431">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4431">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4432">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4432">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4433">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4433">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4434">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4434">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4435">Регулярное выражение Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4435">The regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4436">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4436">A keyword from Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland European Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="60f75aed-81bf-4625-89b0-0846b9248ee7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4454">Национальный идентификатор Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4454">Finland national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4455">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4455">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4456">шесть цифр плюс символ, указывающий на столетие плюс три цифры плюс контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4456">six digits plus a character indicating a century plus three digits plus a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4457">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4457">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4458">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4458">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4459">шесть цифр в формате формата ддммгг —, представляющие собой дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4459">six digits in the format format DDMMYY which are a date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4460">маркер века ("-", "+" или "a")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4460">century marker (either '-', '+' or 'a')</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4461">трехзначный идентификационный номер, соличный с тремя цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4461">three-digit personal identification number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4462">цифра или буква (без учета регистра), которая является контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4462">a digit or letter (case insensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4463">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4463">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4464">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4464">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4465">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4465">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4466">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4466">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4467">Функция Func_finnish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4467">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4468">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_finnish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4468">a keyword from Keyword_finnish_national_id is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4469">Контрольная сумма проходит</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4469">the checksum passes</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4470">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4470">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4471">Функция Func_finnish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4471">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4472">Контрольная сумма проходит</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4472">the checksum passes</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finnish National ID-->
      <Entity id="338FD995-4CB5-4F87-AD35-79BD1DD926C1" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4473">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4473">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4475">хенкилöкохтаинен туннус</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4475">henkilökohtainen tunnus</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4478">хенкилöтуннуснумеро</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4478">henkilötunnusnumero</span></span>

## <a name="finland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4521">Номер паспорта для Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4521">Finland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4522">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4522">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4523">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4523">Format</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4524">сочетание девяти букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4524">combination of nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4525">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4525">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4526">сочетание девяти букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4526">combination of nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4527">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4527">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4528">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4528">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4529">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4529">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4530">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4530">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4531">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4531">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4532">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4532">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4533">регулярное выражение Regex_finland_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4533">The regular expression Regex_finland_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4534">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_eu_passport_number_common или Keyword_finland_passport_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4534">A keyword from Keywords_eu_passport_number_common or Keyword_finland_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Finland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="d1685ac3-1d3a-40f8-8198-32ef5669c7a5" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4535">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4535">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number_common"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4536">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4536">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4543">пасспортнумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4543">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4544">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4544">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4545">пасспортнумберс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4545">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4546">номера паспортов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4546">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_finland_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4547">Keyword_finland_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4547">Keyword_finland_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4548">суомалаинен Пасси</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4548">suomalainen passi</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4549">транзитный нумеро</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4549">passin numero</span></span>

## <a name="finland-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4555">Номер социального страхования для Финляндии или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4555">Finland social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4556">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4556">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4557">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4557">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4558">11 символов в указанном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4558">An 11-character combination in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4559">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4559">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4560">сочетание из 11 символов в указанном формате:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4560">an 11-character combination in the specified format:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4561">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4561">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4562">один из следующих экземпляров:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4562">one instance of one of the following:</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4563">символ "плюс"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4563">plus symbol</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4564">символ "минус"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4564">minus symbol</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4565">буква "A" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4565">the letter "A" (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4566">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4566">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4567">одна буква или одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4567">one letter or one digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4568">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4568">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4569">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4569">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4570">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4570">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4571">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4571">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4572">Функция  `Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4572">The function  `Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4573">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4573">A keyword from  `Keywords_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4574">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4574">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4575">Функция  `Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4575">The function  `Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4576">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4576">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4577">Keywords_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4577">Keywords_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4578">identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4578">identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4579">личный идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4579">personal id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4580">идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4580">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4581">Финский национальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4581">finnish national id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4582">персоналиднумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4582">personalidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4583">national identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4583">national identification number</span></span>

## <a name="france-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4599">Номер водительского удостоверения для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4599">France driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4600">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера водительского удостоверения для ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4600">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4601">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4601">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4602">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4602">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4603">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4603">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4604">12 цифр с проверкой подлинности, чтобы избежать путаницы с похожими шаблонами, например французскими номерами телефонов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4604">12 digits with validation to discount similar patterns such as French telephone numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4605">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4605">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4606">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4606">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4607">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4607">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4608">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4608">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4609">Функция Func_french_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4609">the function Func_french_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4610">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_french_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4610">a keyword from Keyword_french_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="18e55a36-a01b-4b0f-943d-dc10282a1824" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_french_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4737">Номер страховки для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4737">France health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4738">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4738">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4739">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4739">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4740">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4740">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4741">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4741">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4742">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4742">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4743">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4743">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4744">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4744">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4745">21 цифра цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4745">21 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4746">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4746">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4747">21 цифра:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4747">21 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4748">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4748">ten digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4749">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4749">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4750">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4750">ten digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4751">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4751">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4752">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4752">a digit</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4753">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4753">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4754">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4754">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4755">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4755">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4756">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4756">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4757">регулярное выражение Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4757">the regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4758">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4758">a keyword from Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="9bc2069e-76df-4ff9-ac02-2f519469e236" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4759">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4759">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_health_insurance_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4760">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4760">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4761">Карточка страхования</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4761">insurance card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4762">Витале корзины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4762">carte vitale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4763">Корзина д'ассурé социальных сетей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4763">carte d'assuré social</span></span>


## <a name="france-national-id-card-cni"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4764">Национальный идентификационный номер страны Франции (CNI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4764">France national id card (CNI)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4765">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4765">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4766">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4766">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4767">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4767">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4768">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4768">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4769">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4769">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4770">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4770">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4771">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4771">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4772">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4772">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4773">регулярное выражение Regex_france_cni находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4773">The regular expression Regex_france_cni finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4774">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4774">A keyword from Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France CNI -->
    <Entity id="f741ac74-1bc0-4665-b69b-f0c7f927c0c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="65">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_france_cni" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4775">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4775">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_france_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4776">Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4776">Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4777">card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4777">card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4778">Национальный д'идентитé для корзины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4778">carte nationale d’identité</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4779">Национальный д'идените для корзины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4779">carte nationale d'idenite no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4780">CNI #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4780">cni#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4781">CNI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4781">cni</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4782">Компте банкаире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4782">compte bancaire</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4783">national identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4783">national identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4784">Национальная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4784">national identity</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4785">натионалидно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4785">nationalidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4786">нумéро д'ассуранце маладие</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4786">numéro d'assurance maladie</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4787">нумéро де корзина Витале</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4787">numéro de carte vitale</span></span>

   
## <a name="france-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4788">Номер паспорта для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4788">France passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4789">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4789">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4790">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4790">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4791">девять цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4791">nine digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4792">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4792">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4793">девять цифр и букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4793">nine digits and letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4794">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4794">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4795">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4795">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4796">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4796">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4797">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4797">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4798">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4798">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4799">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4799">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4800">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4800">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4801">функция Func_fr_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4801">The function Func_fr_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4802">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4802">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France Passport Number -->
<Entity id="3008b884-8c8c-4cd8-a289-99f34fc7ff5d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4803">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4803">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4804">Keyword_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4804">Keyword_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4805">Passport Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4805">Passport Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4806">Passport No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4806">Passport No</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4807">Passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4807">Passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4808">Службу #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4808">Passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4809">пасспортид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4809">PassportID</span></span>
