## <a name="france-social-security-number-insee-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4823">Номер социального страхования для Франции (INSEE) или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4823">France social security number (INSEE) or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4824">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в номер социального страхования ЕС и эквивалентный тип конфиденциальной информации и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4824">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Social Security Number and Equivalent ID sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4825">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4825">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4826">15 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4826">15 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4827">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4827">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4828">Должен соответствовать одному из двух шаблонов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4828">Must match one of two patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4829">13 цифр, за которыми следует пробел, за которым следуют две цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4829">13 digits followed by a space followed by two digits</span></span><br/>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4830">или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4830">or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4831">15 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4831">15 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4832">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4832">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4833">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4833">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4834">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4834">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4835">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4835">A DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4836">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4836">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4837">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4837">A keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4838">контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4838">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4839">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4839">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4840">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4840">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4841">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee не находится;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4841">No keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4842">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4842">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France INSEE -->
<Entity id="71f62b97-efe0-4aa1-aa49-e14de253619d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="france-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4868">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4868">France tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4869">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4869">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4870">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4870">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4871">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4871">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4872">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4872">13 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4873">Одна цифра, которая должна быть равна 0, 1, 2 или 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4873">One digit that must be 0, 1, 2, or 3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4874">1 цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4874">1 digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4875">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4875">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4876">2 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4876">2 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4877">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4877">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4878">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4878">3 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4879">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4879">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4880">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4880">3 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4881">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4881">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4882">3 контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4882">3 check digits</span></span> 

  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4883">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4883">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4884">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4884">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4885">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4885">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4886">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4886">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4887">Функция  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4887">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4888">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4888">A keyword from  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4889">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4889">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4890">Функция  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4890">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- France Tax Identification Number (numéro SPI.) -->
      <Entity id="ed59e77e-171d-442c-9ec1-88e2ebcb5b0a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4897">налог без #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4897">tax no#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4904">таксно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4904">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4905">такснумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4905">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4906">такснумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4906">taxnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4907">Идентификатор Tin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4907">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4908">номер Tin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4908">tin no</span></span>

## <a name="france-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4910">Значение налогового номера, добавленного в Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4910">France value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4911">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4911">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4912">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4912">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4913">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4913">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4914">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4914">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4915">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4915">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4916">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4916">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4917">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4917">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4918">13-буквенно-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4918">13 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4919">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4919">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4920">13 символов буквенно-цифрового шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4920">13 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4921">две буквы — FR (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4921">two letters  - FR (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4922">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4922">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4923">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4923">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4924">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4924">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4925">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4925">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4926">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4926">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4927">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4927">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4928">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4928">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4929">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4929">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4930">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4930">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4931">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4931">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4932">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4932">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4933">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4933">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4934">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4934">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4935">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4935">A keyword from Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4936">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4936">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4937">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4937">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="949121e6-ad9f-4379-8731-710342baea78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4938">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4938">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4939">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4939">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4940">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4940">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4941">НДС No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4941">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4942">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4942">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4943">налог на добавленную стоимость</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4943">value added tax</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4944">Siren идентификация No нумéро д'идентификатион таксе Сур валеур ажаутéе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4944">siren identification no numéro d'identification taxe sur valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4945">таксе валеур ажаутéе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4945">taxe valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4946">таксе Сур Ла валеур ажаутéе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4946">taxe sur la valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4947">n ° тва</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4947">n° tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4948">нумéро de тва</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4948">numéro de tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4949">нумéро д'идентификатион Siren</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4949">numéro d'identification siren</span></span>


## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4950">Номер водительского удостоверения для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4950">Germany driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4951">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4951">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4952">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4952">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4953">сочетание 11 цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4953">combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4954">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4954">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4955">11 цифр и букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4955">11 digits and letters (not case sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4956">цифра или буква;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4956">a digit or letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4957">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4957">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4958">шесть цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4958">six digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4959">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4959">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4960">цифра или буква;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4960">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4961">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4961">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4962">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4962">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4963">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4963">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4964">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4964">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4965">Функция Func_german_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4965">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4966">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_german_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4966">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-4967">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-4967">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5116">Номер идентификационной карточки для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5116">Germany identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5117">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5117">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5118">с 1 ноября 2010: девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5118">since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5119">от 1 апреля 1987 до 31 октября 2010:10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5119">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5120">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5120">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5121">с 1 ноября 2010:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5121">since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5122">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5122">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5123">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5123">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5124">от 1 апреля 1987 до 31 октября 2010:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5124">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5125">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5125">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5126">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5126">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5127">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5127">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5128">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5128">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5129">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5129">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5130">регулярное выражение Regex_germany_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5130">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5131">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_germany_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5131">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5132">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5132">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5133">Keyword_germany_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5133">Keyword_germany_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5134">аусвеис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5134">ausweis</span></span>

## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5147">Номер паспорта для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5147">Germany passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5148">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5148">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5149">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5149">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5150">десять цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5150">ten digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5151">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5151">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5152">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5152">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5153">Первый символ — цифра или буква из этого набора (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5153">first character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5154">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5154">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5155">пять цифр или букв из этого набора (C,-H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5155">five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5156">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5156">a digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5157">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5157">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5158">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5158">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5159">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5159">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5160">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5160">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5161">функция Func_german_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5161">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5162">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keyword_german_passport` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5162">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5163">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5163">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5164">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5164">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5165">функция Func_german_passport_data находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5165">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5166">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keyword_german_passport` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5166">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5167">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5167">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5168">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5168">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_german_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5169">Keyword_german_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5169">Keyword_german_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5170">реисепассе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5170">reisepasse</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5171">реисепасснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5171">reisepassnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5172">No-Reisepass</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5172">No-Reisepass</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5173">Nr-Reisepass</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5173">Nr-Reisepass</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5174">Reisepass-Nr</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5174">Reisepass-Nr</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5175">пасснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5175">Passnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5176">реисепäссе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5176">reisepässe</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5177">пассепорт но.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5177">passeport no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5178">пассепорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5178">passeport no</span></span>

## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5179">Идентификационный номер налогоплательщика (Германия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5179">Germany tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5180">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5180">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5181">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5181">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5182">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5182">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5183">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5183">11 digits :</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5184">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5184">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5185">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5185">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5186">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5186">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5187">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5187">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5188">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5188">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5189">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5189">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5190">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5190">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5191">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5191">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5192">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5192">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5193">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5193">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5194">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5194">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5195">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5195">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5196">Функция  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5196">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5197">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5197">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5198">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5198">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5199">Функция  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5199">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Germany Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="43316a89-9880-40cf-b980-04bc7eefcec5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5209">налог без #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5209">tax no#</span></span>

## <a name="germany-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5225">Значение налогового номера добавленного в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5225">Germany value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5226">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5226">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5227">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5227">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5228">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5228">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5229">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5229">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5230">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5230">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5231">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5231">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5232">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5232">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5233">11 буквенно-цифрового шаблона</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5233">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5234">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5234">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5235">11-буквенно-цифровой буквенно-значный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5235">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5236">буква D или d</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5236">a letter D or d</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5237">буква E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5237">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5238">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5238">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5239">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5239">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5240">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5240">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5241">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5241">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5242">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5242">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5243">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5243">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5244">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5244">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5245">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5245">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5246">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5246">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5247">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5247">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5248">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5248">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5249">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5249">A keyword from Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5250">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5250">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5251">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5251">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="db177eb2-8811-4842-bffc-128c14aa219f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5254">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5254">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5255">НДС No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5255">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5256">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5256">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5257">НДС # мехрвертстеуер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5257">vat#  mehrwertsteuer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5258">мвст</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5258">mwst</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5259">мехрвертстеуер идентификатионснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5259">mehrwertsteuer identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5260">мехрвертстеуер нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5260">mehrwertsteuer nummer</span></span>


## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5261">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5261">Greece driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5262">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5262">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5263">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5263">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5264">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5264">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5265">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5265">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5266">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5266">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5267">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5267">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5268">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5268">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5269">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5269">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5270">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5270">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5271">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5271">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5272">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5272">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="7a2200b5-aacf-4e3c-ab36-136d3e68b7da" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-national-id-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5398">Национальный идентификационный номер карты (Греция)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5398">Greece national ID card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5399">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5399">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5400">Сочетание 7–8 букв и чисел, а также тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5400">Combination of 7-8 letters and numbers plus a dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5401">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5401">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5402">Семь букв и чисел (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5402">Seven letters and numbers (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5403">одна буква (любая буква греческого алфавита);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5403">One letter (any letter of the Greek alphabet)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5404">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5404">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5405">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5405">Six digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5406">Восемь букв и чисел (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5406">Eight letters and numbers (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5407">две буквы, которые в прописном виде есть как в греческом, так и латинском алфавите (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5407">Two letters whose uppercase character occurs in both the Greek and Latin alphabets (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5408">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5408">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5409">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5409">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5410">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5410">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5411">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5411">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5412">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5412">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5413">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5413">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5414">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5414">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5415">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_greece_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5415">A keyword from Keyword_greece_id_card is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5416">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5416">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5417">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5417">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece National ID Card -->
      <Entity id="82568215-1da1-46d3-874a-d2294d81b5ac" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5418">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5418">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_greece_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5419">Keyword_greece_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5419">Keyword_greece_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5420">Греческий идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5420">greek id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5421">Греческая национальная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5421">greek national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5422">Греческая личная идентификационная карточка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5422">greek personal id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5423">код греческой политики</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5423">greek police id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5424">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5424">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5425">таутотита</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5425">tautotita</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5426">ταυτότητα</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5426">ταυτότητα</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5427">ταυτότητας</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5427">ταυτότητας</span></span>


## <a name="greece-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5428">Номер паспорта для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5428">Greece passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5429">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5429">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5430">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5430">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5431">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5431">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5432">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5432">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5433">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5433">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5434">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5434">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5435">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5435">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5436">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5436">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5437">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5437">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5438">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5438">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5439">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5439">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5440">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5440">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number_common"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5441">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5441">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5444">пасспортид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5444">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5445">паспорты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5445">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5446">пасспортно</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5446">passportno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5447">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5447">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5448">пасспортнумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5448">passportnumber</span></span>

## <a name="greece-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5456">Идентификационный номер налога в Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5456">Greece tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5457">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5457">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5458">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5458">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5459">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5459">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5460">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5460">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5461">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5461">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5462">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5462">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5463">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5463">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5464">Девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5464">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5465">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5465">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5466">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5466">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5467">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5467">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5468">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5468">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5469">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5469">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5470">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5470">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5471">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5471">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5472">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5472">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greek Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="15a54a5a-53d4-4080-ad43-a2a4fe1d3bf7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hong-kong-identity-card-hkid-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5501">Номер идентификационной карточки Гонконг (HKID)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5501">Hong Kong identity card (HKID) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5502">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5502">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5503">Сочетание 8–9 букв и чисел, а также необязательные скобки вокруг последнего символа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5503">Combination of 8-9 letters and numbers plus optional parentheses around the final character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5504">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5504">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5505">Сочетание 8–9 букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5505">Combination of 8-9 letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5506">1–2 буквы (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5506">1-2 letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5507">шесть цифр; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5507">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5508">последний символ (любая цифра или буква "A") является проверочной цифрой и заключен в скобки (необязательно).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5508">The final character (any digit or the letter A), which is the check digit and is optionally enclosed in parentheses.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5509">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5509">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5510">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5510">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5511">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5511">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5512">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5512">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5513">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5513">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5514">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_hong_kong_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5514">A keyword from Keyword_hong_kong_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5515">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5515">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5516">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5516">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5517">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5517">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5518">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5518">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Hong Kong Identity Card (HKID) number -->
<Entity id="e63c28a7-ad29-4c17-a41a-3d2a0b70fd9c" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5558">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5558">Hungary driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5559">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5559">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5560">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5560">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5561">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5561">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5562">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5562">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5563">Две буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5563">Two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5564">Две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5564">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5565">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5565">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5566">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5566">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5567">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5567">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5568">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5568">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5569">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5569">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5570">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5570">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5571">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5571">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <Entity id="9d31c46b-6e6b-444c-aeb1-6dd7e604bb24" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5696">Венгрия персональный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5696">Hungary personal identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5697">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5697">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5698">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5698">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5699">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5699">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5700">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5700">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5701">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5701">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5702">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5702">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5703">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5703">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5704">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5704">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5705">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5705">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5706">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5706">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5707">Одна цифра, соответствующая пол (1-м-штекер, 2-гнездо, другие номера также могут иметь гражданские телефоны перед 1900 или гражданами с удвоенной гражданией)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5707">One digit that corresponds to gender (1-male, 2-female, other numbers are also possible for citizens born before 1900 or citizens with double citizenship)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5708">Шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5708">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5709">Три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5709">Three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5710">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5710">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5711">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5711">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5712">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5712">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5713">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5713">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5714">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5714">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5715">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5715">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5716">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5716">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5717">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5717">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5718">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5718">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="7b5cc218-7046-47d9-80c9-f325b50896ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5722">identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5722">identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5723">СЗ IG</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5723">sz ig</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5724">СЗ.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5724">sz.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5725">IG.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5725">ig.</span></span>

## <a name="hungary-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5729">Номер паспорта для Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5729">Hungary passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5730">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5730">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5731">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5731">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5732">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть или семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5732">Two letters followed by six or seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5733">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5733">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5734">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть или семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5734">Two letters followed by six or seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5735">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5735">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5736">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5736">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5737">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5737">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5738">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5738">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5739">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5739">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5740">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5740">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5741">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5741">Keywords</span></span>
