## <a name="hungary-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5757">Венгерский номер социального страхования или идентификация эквивалентных прав</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5757">Hungary social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5758">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5758">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5759">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5759">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5760">Девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5760">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5761">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5761">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5762">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5762">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5763">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5763">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5764">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5764">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5765">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5765">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5766">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5766">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5767">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5767">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5768">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5768">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5769">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5769">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5770">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5770">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5790">Идентификационный номер венгерского налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5790">Hungary tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5791">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5791">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5792">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5792">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5793">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5793">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5794">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5794">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5795">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5795">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5796">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5796">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5797">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5797">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5798">Десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5798">Ten digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5799">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5799">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5800">Десять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5800">Ten digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5801">Одна цифра, которая должна быть "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5801">One digit that must be "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5802">восемь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5802">Eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5803">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5803">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5804">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5804">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5805">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5805">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5806">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5806">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5807">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5807">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5808">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5808">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5809">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5809">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5810">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5810">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5811">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5811">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="ede42eb4-59d9-49eb-9603-d7853fbda91d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5837">Венгерский номер добавленного значения налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5837">Hungary value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5838">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5838">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5839">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5839">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5840">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5840">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5841">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5841">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5842">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5842">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5843">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5843">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5844">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5844">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5845">10-буквенно-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5845">10 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5846">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5846">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5847">10 буквенно-цифровых буквенных символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5847">10 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5848">2 буквы — HU или HU</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5848">2 letters - HU or hu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5849">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5849">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5850">8 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5850">8 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5851">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5851">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5852">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5852">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5853">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5853">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5854">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5854">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5855">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5855">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5856">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5856">A keyword from Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5857">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5857">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5858">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5858">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="976349a0-683b-477a-90f8-ff0a220d5592" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5859">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5859">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_hungary_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5860">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5860">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5864">ватно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5864">vatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5865">хунгарианватно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5865">hungarianvatno#</span></span>

## <a name="india-permanent-account-number-pan"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5872">Номер постоянного счета Индии (PAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5872">India permanent account number (PAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5873">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5873">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5874">10 букв или цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5874">10 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5875">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5875">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5876">10 букв или цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5876">10 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5877">Три буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5877">Three letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5878">Буква в C, P, H, F, A, T, B, L, J, G (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5878">A letter in C, P, H, F, A, T, B, L, J, G (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5879">Буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5879">A letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5880">Четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5880">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5881">Буква (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5881">A letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5882">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5882">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5883">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5883">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5884">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5884">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5885">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5885">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5886">регулярное выражение Regex_india_permanent_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5886">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5887">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_india_permanent_account_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5887">A keyword from Keyword_india_permanent_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5888">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5888">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5889">регулярное выражение Regex_india_permanent_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5889">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- India Permanent Account Number -->
      <Entity id="2602bfee-9bb0-47a5-a7a6-2bf3053e2804" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_india_permanent_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3520.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5890">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5890">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_india_permanent_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5891">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5891">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5892">Permanent Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5892">Permanent Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5893">ПАНОРАМИРОВАНИЕ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5893">PAN</span></span> 
   
## <a name="india-unique-identification-aadhaar-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5894">Уникальный идентификационный номер (Aadhaar) Индии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5894">India unique identification (Aadhaar) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5895">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5895">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5896">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы или тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5896">12 digits containing optional spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5897">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5897">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5898">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5898">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5899">Цифра, не равная 0 или 1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5899">A digit which is not 0 or 1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5900">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5900">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5901">необязательный пробел или тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5901">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5902">четыре цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5902">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5903">необязательный пробел или тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5903">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5904">последняя цифра — проверочная.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5904">The final digit which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5905">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5905">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5906">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5906">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5907">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5907">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5908">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5908">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5909">функция Func_india_aadhaar находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5909">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5910">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_india_aadhar;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5910">A keyword from Keyword_india_aadhar is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5911">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5911">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- 
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5912">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5912">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5913">функция Func_india_aadhaar находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5913">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5914">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5914">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- India Unique Identification (Aadhaar) number -->
<Entity id="1ca46b29-76f5-4f46-9383-cfa15e91048f" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_india_aadhar"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_india_aadhar"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5916">Keyword_india_aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5916">Keyword_india_aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5917">aadhaar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5917">aadhaar</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5919">аадхар #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5919">aadhar#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5920">uid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5920">uid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5921">आधार</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5921">आधार</span></span>

## <a name="indonesia-identity-card-ktp-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5923">Номер идентификационной карточки Индонезия (KTP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5923">Indonesia identity card (KTP) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5924">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5924">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5925">16 цифр, содержащих необязательные точки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5925">16 digits containing optional periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5926">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5926">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5927">16 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5927">16 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5928">две цифры (код провинции);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5928">Two-digit province code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5929">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5929">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5930">две цифры (код округа или города);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5930">Two-digit regency or city code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5931">две цифры (код района);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5931">Two-digit subdistrict code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5932">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5932">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5933">шесть цифр в формате ДДММГГ (дата рождения);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5933">Six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5934">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5934">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5935">четыре цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5935">Four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5936">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5936">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5937">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5937">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5938">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5938">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5939">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5939">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5940">регулярное выражение Regex_indonesia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5940">The regular expression Regex_indonesia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5941">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_indonesia_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5941">A keyword from Keyword_indonesia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Indonesia Identity Card (KTP) Number -->
<Entity id="da68fdb0-f383-4981-8c86-82689d3b7d55" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_indonesia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_indonesia_id_card"/>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5942">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5942">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_indonesia_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5943">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5943">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5944">KTP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5944">KTP</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5945">Kartu Tanda Penduduk</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5945">Kartu Tanda Penduduk</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5946">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5946">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span></span> 
   
## <a name="international-banking-account-number-iban"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5947">Международный номер банковского счета (IBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5947">International banking account number (IBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5948">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5948">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5949">Код страны (две буквы), а также проверочные цифры (две) и номер bban (до 30 символов)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5949">Country code (two letters) plus check digits (two digits) plus bban number (up to 30 characters)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5950">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5950">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5951">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5951">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5952">Двухбуквенный код страны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5952">Two-letter country code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5953">Две проверочные цифры (после которых может следовать пробел) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5953">Two check digits (followed by an optional space)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5954">1–7 групп из четырех букв или цифр (могут разделяться пробелами)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5954">1-7 groups of four letters or digits (can be separated by spaces)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5955">1–3 буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5955">1-3 letters or digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-p133">Формат для названия каждой из стран немного отличается. Тип конфиденциальной информации IBAN применяется к следующим 60 странам:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-p133">The format for each country is slightly different. The IBAN sensitive information type covers these 60 countries:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5958">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5958">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5959">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5959">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5960">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5960">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5961">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5961">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5962">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5962">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5963">функция Func_iban находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5963">The function Func_iban finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5964">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5964">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="e7dc4711-11b7-4cb0-b88b-2c394a771f0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_iban" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-10-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5967">Международная классификация Diseases (ICD-10-CM)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5967">International classification of diseases (ICD-10-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5968">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5968">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5969">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5969">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5970">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5970">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5971">Ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5971">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5972">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5972">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5973">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5973">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5974">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5974">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5975">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5975">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5976">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5976">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5977">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_codes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5977">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5978">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5978">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5979">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_ "Обновлено".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5979">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_ updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- ICD-10 CM -->
      <Entity id="3356946c-6bb7-449b-b253-6ffa419c0ce7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
        </Pattern>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5980">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5980">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5981">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_10_updated ключевых слов, основанный на [международной классификации Diseases, десятой версии, Клиникал модификации (ICD-10-cm)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5981">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5982">Этот тип ищет только термин, а не коды страхования.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5982">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5983">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_10_codes ключевых слов, основанный на [международной классификации Diseases, десятой версии, Клиникал модификации (ICD-10-cm)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5983">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5984">Этот тип ищет только страховые коды, а не описание.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5984">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5987">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5987">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5992">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5992">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5993">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5993">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5994">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5994">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5995">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_codes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5995">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5996">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5996">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5997">Найдено ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5997">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <Entity id="fa3f9c74-ee07-4c52-b5f2-085d6b2c0ec4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5998">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5998">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-5999">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_9_updated ключевых слов, основанный на [международной классификации Diseases, девятой редакции, Клиникал модификации (ICD-9-cm)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-5999">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6000">Этот тип ищет только термин, а не коды страхования.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6000">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6001">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_9_codes ключевых слов, основанный на [международной классификации Diseases, девятой редакции, Клиникал модификации (ICD-9-cm)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6001">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6002">Этот тип ищет только страховые коды, а не описание.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6002">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="ip-address"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6003">IP-адрес</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6003">IP address</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6004">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6004">Format</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv4"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6005">IPv4</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6005">IPv4:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6006">Сложный шаблон, ответственный за форматированные (с точками) и неформатированные (без точек) версии IPv4-адресов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6006">Complex pattern which accounts for formatted (periods) and unformatted (no periods) versions of the IPv4 addresses</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv6"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6007">Поддерживающ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6007">IPv6:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6008"> Сложный шаблон, ответственный за форматированные номера IPv6 (вместе с двоеточиями).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6008">Complex pattern which accounts for formatted IPv6 numbers (which include colons)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6009">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6009">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6010">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6010">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6011">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6011">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6012">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6012">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6013">В случае с протоколом IPv6 политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6013">For IPv6, a DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6014">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv6_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6014">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6015">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6015">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6016">В случае с протоколом IPv4 политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6016">For IPv4, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6017">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv4_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6017">The regular expression Regex_ipv4_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6018">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6018">A keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6019">В случае с протоколом IPv6 политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6019">For IPv6, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6020">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv6_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6020">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6021">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6021">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- IP Address -->
    <Entity id="1daa4ad5-e2dd-4ca4-a788-54722c09efb2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv4_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6022">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6022">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ipaddress"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6023">Keyword_ipaddress</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6023">Keyword_ipaddress</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6024">IP (ключевое слово с учетом регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6024">IP (this keyword is case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6025">ip address</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6025">ip address</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6026">ip addresses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6026">ip addresses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6027">internet protocol</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6027">internet protocol</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6028">IP-כתובת ה</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6028">IP-כתובת ה</span></span> 

## <a name="ireland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6029">Номер водительского удостоверения для Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6029">Ireland driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6030">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6030">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6031">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6031">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6032">Шесть цифр, за которыми следуют четыре буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6032">Six digits followed by four letters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6033">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6033">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6034">Шесть цифр и четыре буквы:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6034">Six digits and four letters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6035">Шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6035">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6036">Четыре буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6036">Four letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6037">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6037">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6038">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6038">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6039">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6039">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6040">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6040">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6041">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6041">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6042">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6042">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="e01bccd9-eb4d-414f-ace1-e9b6a4c4a2ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6166">Номер паспорта для Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6166">Ireland passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6167">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6167">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6168">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6168">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6169">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6169">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6170">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6170">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6171">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6171">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6172">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6172">Two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6173">семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6173">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6174">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6174">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6175">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6175">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6176">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6176">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6177">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6177">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6178">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6178">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6179">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6179">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-personal-public-service-pps-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6200">Номер личной общедоступной службы (PPS) Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6200">Ireland personal public service (PPS) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6201">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6201">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6202">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6202">Old format (until 31 Dec 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6203">семь цифр, за которыми следует 1-2 букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6203">seven digits followed by 1-2 letters</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6204">Новый формат (1 января 2013 и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6204">New format (1 Jan 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6205">семь цифр, за которыми следуют две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6205">seven digits followed by two letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6206">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6206">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6207">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6207">Old format (until 31 Dec 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6208">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6208">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6209">одна-2 буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6209">one to two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6210">Новый формат (1 января 2013 и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6210">New format (1 Jan 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6211">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6211">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6212">буква (без учета регистра), которая является буквенной контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6212">a letter (not case sensitive) which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6213">Необязательная буква в диапазоне A – I или "W"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6213">An optional letter in the range A-I, or “W”</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6214">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6214">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6215">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6215">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6216">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6216">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6217">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6217">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6218">Функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6218">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6219">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6219">A keyword from Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6220">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6220">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6221">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6221">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6222">функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6222">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6223">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6223">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ireland Personal Public Service (PPS) Number -->
      <Entity id="1cdb674d-c19a-4fcf-9f4b-7f56cc87345a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="israel-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6268">Номер банковского счета для Израиля</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6268">Israel bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6269">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6269">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6270">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6270">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6271">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6271">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6272">Форматируемые</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6272">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6273">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6273">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6274">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6274">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6275">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6275">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6276">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6276">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6277">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6277">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6278">Неформатированные</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6278">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6279">	13 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6279">13 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6280">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6280">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6281">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6281">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6282">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6282">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6283">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6283">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6284">регулярное выражение Regex_israel_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6284">The regular expression Regex_israel_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6285">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_israel_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6285">A keyword from Keyword_israel_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="7d08b2ff-a0b9-437f-957c-aeddbf9b2b25" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_israel_bank_account_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_israel_bank_account_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6286">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6286">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6287">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6287">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6288">Bank Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6288">Bank Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6289">Bank Account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6289">Bank Account</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6290">Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6290">Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6291">מספר חשבון בנק</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6291">מספר חשבון בנק</span></span> 
   
## <a name="israel-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6292">Национальный идентификационный номер Израиля</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6292">Israel national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6293">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6293">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6294">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6294">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6295">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6295">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6296">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6296">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6297">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6297">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6298">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6298">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6299">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6299">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6300">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6300">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6301">функция Func_israeli_national_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6301">The function Func_israeli_national_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6302">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Israel_National_ID;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6302">A keyword from Keyword_Israel_National_ID is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6303">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6303">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel National ID Number -->
<Entity id="e05881f5-1db1-418c-89aa-a3ac5c5277ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_israeli_national_id_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Israel_National_ID" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

-   <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6309">זהותישר אלית</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6309">זהותישר אלית</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6310">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6310">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6311">هوية إسرائ يلية</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6311">هوية إسرائ يلية</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6312">رقم الهوية</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6312">رقم الهوية</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6313">عدد هوية فريدة من نوعها</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6313">عدد هوية فريدة من نوعها</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6315">идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6315">id number</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6316">Идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6316">identity no</span></span>        
-   <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6317">идентитинумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6317">identitynumber#</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6318">идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6318">identity number</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6319">исраелиидентитинумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6319">israeliidentitynumber</span></span>       
-   <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6320">личный идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6320">personal id</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6321">уникальный идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6321">unique id</span></span>  

   
## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6322">Номер водительского удостоверения для Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6322">Italy driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6323">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6323">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6324">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6324">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6325">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6325">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6326">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6326">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6327">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6327">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6328">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6328">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6329">буква "A" или "V" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6329">the letter "A" or "V" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6330">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6330">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6331">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6331">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6332">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6332">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6333">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6333">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6334">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6334">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6335">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6335">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6336">регулярное выражение Regex_italy_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6336">The regular expression Regex_italy_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6337">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6337">A keyword from Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
<Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6338">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6338">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6339">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6339">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span></span>
