- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6344">патенти GUID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6344">patenti guida</span></span>

## <a name="italy-fiscal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6345">Финансовый код Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6345">Italy fiscal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6346">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6346">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6347">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6347">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6348">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6348">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6349">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6349">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6350">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6350">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6351">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6351">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6352">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6352">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6353">16 – символическое сочетание букв и цифр в указанном шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6353">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6354">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6354">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6355">16 – буквенное сочетание букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6355">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6356">три буквы, соответствующие первым трем согласным в имени семейства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6356">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6357">три буквы, соответствующие первым, третьим и четвертым согласным в имени.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6357">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6358">две цифры, соответствующие последним цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6358">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6359">одна буква, соответствующая букве дня рождения, буквы используются в алфавитном порядке, но используются только буквы от A до E, H, L, M, P, R — T (то есть Январь — это R, а Октябрь — R)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6359">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (thus, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6360">две цифры, которые соответствуют дню месяца рождения, для различения пола, 40 добавляется в день рождения для женщин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6360">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth—in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6361">четыре цифры, соответствующие коду города, который относится к органу государственной власти, в котором был создан пользователь, (для иностранных стран используются коды уровня страны).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6361">four digits that corresponds to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6362">одна цифра четности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6362">one parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6363">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6363">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6364">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6364">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6365">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6365">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6366">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6366">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6367">Функция  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6367">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6368">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6368">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6369">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6369">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6370">Функция  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6370">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6405">Номер паспорта для Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6405">Italy passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6406">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6406">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6407">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6407">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6408">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6408">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6409">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6409">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6410">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6410">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6411">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6411">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6412">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6412">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6413">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6413">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6414">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6414">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6415">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6415">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6416">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6416">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6417">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6417">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6418">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6418">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6419">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6419">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6427">пасспортнумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6427">passportnumber</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6430">номера паспортов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6430">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_italy_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6431">Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6431">Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6432">Итальянский пассапорто</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6432">italiana passaporto</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6433">пассапорто итальянский</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6433">passaporto italiana</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6434">пассапорто нумеро</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6434">passaporto numero</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6435">нумéро пассепорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6435">numéro passeport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6436">Нумеро di пассапорто</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6436">numero di passaporto</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6437">нумери del пассапорто</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6437">numeri del passaporto</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6438">пассепорт италиен</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6438">passeport italien</span></span>

## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6439">Налоговый номер добавленной стоимости (Италия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6439">Italy value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6440">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6440">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6441">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6441">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6442">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6442">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6443">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6443">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6444">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6444">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6445">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6445">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6446">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6446">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6447">13-буквенно-цифровой буквенный шаблон с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6447">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6448">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6448">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6449">13-буквенно-цифровой буквенно-цифровой шаблон с необязательными ограничителями:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6449">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6450">I или i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6450">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6451">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6451">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6452">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6452">optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6453">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6453">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6454">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6454">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6455">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6455">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6456">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6456">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6457">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6457">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6458">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6458">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6459">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6459">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6460">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6460">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6461">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6461">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6466">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6466">vat#</span></span>

## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6469">Номер банковского счета для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6469">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6470">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6470">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6471">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6471">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6472">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6472">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6473">номер банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6473">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6474">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6474">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6475">код филиала банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6475">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6476">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6476">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6477">пробел или тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6477">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6478">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6478">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6479">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6479">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6480">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6480">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6481">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6481">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6482">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6482">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6483">Функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6483">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6484">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6484">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6485">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6485">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6486">функция Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6486">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6487">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6487">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6488">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6488">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6489">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6489">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6490">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6490">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6537">Номер водительского удостоверения для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6537">Japan driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6538">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6538">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6539">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6539">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6540">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6540">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6541">12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6541">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6542">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6542">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6543">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6543">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6544">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6544">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6545">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6545">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6546">функция Func_jp_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6546">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6547">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6547">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6548">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6548">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6550">дриверлиценсе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6550">driverlicense</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6551">дриверслиценсе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6551">driverslicense</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6552">дривер'слиценсе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6552">driver'slicense</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6553">дриверслиценсес</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6553">driverslicenses</span></span>

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6585">Мой номер для Японии — корпоративный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6585">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6586">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6586">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6587">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6587">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6588">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6588">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6589">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6589">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6590">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6590">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6591">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6591">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6592">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6592">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6593">13 цифра, цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6593">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6594">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6594">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6595">13 цифра:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6595">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6596">одна цифра от 1 до девяти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6596">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6597">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6597">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6598">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6598">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6599">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6599">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6600">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6600">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6601">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6601">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6602">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6602">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6603">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6603">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6604">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6604">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6605">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6605">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6606">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6606">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_japan_my_number_corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6607">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6607">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6608">корпоративный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6608">corporate number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6610">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6610">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6611">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6611">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6612">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6612">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6613">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6613">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6614">個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6614">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6615">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6615">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6616">法人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6616">法人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6617">指定通知書</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6617">指定通知書</span></span>


## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6618">Япония мой номер — личное</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6618">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6619">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6619">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6620">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6620">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6621">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6621">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6622">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6622">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6623">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6623">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6624">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6624">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6625">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6625">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6626">12 цифр номера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6626">12 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6627">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6627">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6628">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6628">12 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6629">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6629">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6630">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6630">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6631">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6631">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6632">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6632">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6633">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6633">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6634">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6634">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6635">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6635">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6636">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6636">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6637">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6637">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6638">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6638">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6639">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6639">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6640">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6640">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6641">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6641">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6642">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6642">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6647">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6647">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6648">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6648">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6649">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6649">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6650">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6650">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6651">個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6651">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6652">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6652">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>

## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6654">Номер паспорта для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6654">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6655">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6655">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6656">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6656">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6657">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6657">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6658">две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6658">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6659">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6659">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6660">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6660">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6661">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6661">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6662">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6662">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6663">функция Func_jp_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6663">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6664">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6664">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6681">Номер карточки для Японии (Япония)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6681">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6682">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6682">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6683">12 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6683">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6684">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6684">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6685">12 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6685">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6686">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6686">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6687">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6687">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6688">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6688">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6689">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6689">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6690">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6690">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6691">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6691">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6692">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6692">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6693">Регулярное выражение Regex_jp_residence_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6693">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6694">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_residence_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6694">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6695">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6695">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6696">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6696">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6697">Номер карточки проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6697">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6698">Номер карточки проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6698">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6699">Карточка проживания #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6699">Residence card #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6700">在留カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6700">在留カード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6701">在留カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6701">在留カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6702">在留番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6702">在留番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6703">Номер резидентного регистрационного номера для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6703">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6704">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6704">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6705">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6705">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6706">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6706">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6707">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6707">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6708">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6708">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6709">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6709">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6710">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6710">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6711">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6711">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6712">функция Func_jp_resident_registration_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6712">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6713">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6713">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6714">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6714">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_resident_registration_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6715">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6715">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6716">Resident Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6716">Resident Registration Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6717">Residents Basic Registry Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6717">Residents Basic Registry Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6718">Resident Registration No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6718">Resident Registration No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6719">Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6719">Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6720">Residents Basic Registry No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6720">Residents Basic Registry No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6721">Basic Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6721">Basic Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6722">外国人登録証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6722">外国人登録証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6723">証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6723">証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6724">登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6724">登録番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6725">外国人登録証</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6725">外国人登録証</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6726">Номер социального страхования для Японии (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6726">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6727">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6727">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6728">7–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6728">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6729">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6729">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6730">7–12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6730">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6731">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6731">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6732">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6732">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6733">шесть цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6733">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6734">7–12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6734">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6735">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6735">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6736">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6736">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6737">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6737">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6738">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6738">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6739">функция Func_jp_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6739">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6740">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6740">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6741">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6741">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6742">функция Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6742">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6743">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6743">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6744">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6744">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6745">Keyword_jp_sin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6745">Keyword_jp_sin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6746">Social Insurance No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6746">Social Insurance No.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6753">雇用保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6753">雇用保険番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6754">保険証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6754">保険証番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6755">社会保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6755">社会保険番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6756">社会保険но.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6756">社会保険No.</span></span>

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6764">Номер водительского удостоверения для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6764">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6765">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6765">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6766">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6766">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6767">три буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6767">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6768">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6768">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6769">три буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6769">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6770">три буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6770">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6771">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6771">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6772">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6772">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6773">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6773">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6774">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6774">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6775">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6775">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6776">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6776">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6777">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6777">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6902">Личный код Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6902">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6903">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6903">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6904">11 цифр и необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6904">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6905">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6905">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6906">Старый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6906">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6907">11 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6907">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6908">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММГГ —)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6908">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6909">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6909">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6910">одна цифра, соответствующая столетию рождения ("0" для 19 века, "1" для 20-й век) и "2" для 21 века)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6910">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6911">четыре цифры, созданные случайным образом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6911">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6912">Новый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6912">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6913">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6913">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6914">Две цифры "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6914">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6915">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6915">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6916">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6916">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6917">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6917">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6918">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6918">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6919">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6919">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6920">Функция  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` или регулярное выражение `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` выполняет поиск содержимого, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6920">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6921">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6921">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6922">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6922">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6923">Функция  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` или регулярное выражение `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` выполняет поиск содержимого, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6923">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6986">Номер паспорта для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6986">Latvia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6987">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6987">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6988">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6988">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6989">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6989">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6990">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6990">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6991">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6991">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6992">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6992">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6993">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6993">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6994">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6994">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6995">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6995">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6996">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6996">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6997">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6997">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6998">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6998">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-6999">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-6999">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7019">Литва номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7019">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7020">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7020">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7021">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7021">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7022">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7022">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7023">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7023">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7024">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7024">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7025">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7025">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7026">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7026">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7027">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7027">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7028">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7028">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7029">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7029">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7030">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7030">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="86f7628b-e0f4-4dc3-9fbc-e4300e4c7d78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7155">Литва персональный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7155">Lithuania personal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7156">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7156">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7157">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7157">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7158">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7158">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7159">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7159">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7160">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7160">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7161">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7161">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7162">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7162">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7163">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7163">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7164">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7164">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7165">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7165">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7166">одна цифра (1-6), соответствующая пол и век рождения человека</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7166">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7167">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7167">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7168">три цифры, которые соответствуют серийному числу даты рождения.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7168">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7169">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7169">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7170">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7170">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7171">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7171">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7172">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7172">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7173">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7173">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7174">Функция  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7174">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7175">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7175">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7176">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7176">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7177">Функция  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7177">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7212">Литва номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7212">Lithuania passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7213">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7213">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7214">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7214">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7215">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7215">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7216">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7216">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7217">восемь цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7217">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7218">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7218">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7219">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7219">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7220">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7220">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7221">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7221">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7222">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7222">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7223">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7223">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
