## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7240">Номер водительского удостоверения Луксембург</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7240">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7241">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7241">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7242">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7242">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7243">шесть цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7243">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7244">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7244">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7245">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7245">six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7246">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7246">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7247">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7247">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7248">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7248">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7249">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7249">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7250">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7250">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7251">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7251">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="89daf717-1544-4860-9a2e-fc9166dd8852" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7375">Национальный идентификационный номер Луксембург (для природных людей)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7375">Luxemburg national identification number (natural persons)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7376">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7376">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7377">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7377">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7378">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7378">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7379">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7379">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7380">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7380">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7381">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7381">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7382">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7382">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7383">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7383">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7384">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7384">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7385">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7385">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7386">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7386">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7387">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7387">two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7388">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7388">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7389">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7389">yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7390">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7390">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7391">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7391">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7392">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7392">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7393">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7393">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7394">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7394">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7395">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7395">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7418">Номер паспорта Луксембург</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7418">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7419">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7419">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7420">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7420">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7421">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7421">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7422">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7422">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7423">восемь цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7423">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7424">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7424">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7425">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7425">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7426">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7426">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7427">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7427">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7428">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_nation_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7428">The regular expression  `Regex_nation_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7429">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7429">A keyword from  `Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_nation_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7430">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7430">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_nation_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7431">Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7431">Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7432">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7432">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7433">номер паспорта для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7433">latvian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7434">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7434">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7435">пасснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7435">passnummer</span></span>

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7436">Луксембург Национальный идентификационный номер (неестественные пользователи)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7436">Luxemburg national identification number (non natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7437">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7437">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7438">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7438">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7439">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7439">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7440">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7440">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7441">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7441">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7442">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7442">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7443">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7443">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7444">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7444">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7445">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7445">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7446">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7446">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7447">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7447">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7448">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7448">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7449">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7449">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7450">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7450">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7451">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7451">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7452">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7452">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7453">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7453">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7454">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7454">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7455">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7455">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7456">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7456">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7496">Идентификационный номер карты Малайзии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7496">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7497">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7497">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7498">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные дефисы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7498">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7499">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7499">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7500">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7500">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7501">шесть цифр в формате ГГММДД Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7501">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7502">тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7502">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7503">код места рождения из двух букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7503">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7504">тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7504">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7505">три случайные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7505">three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7506">код пола из одной цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7506">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7507">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7507">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7508">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7508">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7509">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7509">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7510">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7510">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7511">регулярное выражение Regex_malaysia_id_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7511">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7512">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7512">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7513">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7513">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_malaysia_id_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7514">Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7514">Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7515">карточка цифрового приложения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7515">digital application card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7516">i/c</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7516">i/c</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7517">i/c нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7517">i/c no</span></span>

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7539">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7539">Malta driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7540">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7540">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7541">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7541">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7542">Сочетание двух символов и шести цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7542">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7543">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7543">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7544">сочетание двух символов и шести цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7544">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7545">два символа (цифры или буквы без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7545">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7546">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7546">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7547">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7547">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7548">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7548">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7549">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7549">three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7550">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7550">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7551">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7551">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7552">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7552">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7553">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7553">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7554">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7554">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7555">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7555">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="a3bdaa4a-8371-4735-8fa5-56ee0fb4afc4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7679">Номер идентификационной карточки Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7679">Malta identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7680">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7680">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7681">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7681">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7682">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7682">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7683">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7683">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7684">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7684">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7685">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7685">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7686">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7686">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7687">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7687">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7688">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7688">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7689">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7689">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7690">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7690">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7691">одна буква в письмах "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7691">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7692">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7692">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7693">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7693">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7694">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7694">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7695">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7695">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7696">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7696">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7697">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7697">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7698">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7698">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7699">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7699">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7708">нумру Ta ' идентификаззжони унику</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7708">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7710">нумруные зада сервизз таċ ċиттадин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7710">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span></span>

## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7716">Номер паспорта для Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7716">Malta passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7717">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7717">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7718">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7718">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7719">семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7719">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7720">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7720">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7721">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7721">seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7722">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7722">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7723">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7723">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7724">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7724">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7725">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7725">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7726">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7726">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7727">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7727">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7728">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7728">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7739">номера паспортов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7739">passport numbers</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7741">нумру Тал — пассапорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7741">numru tal-passaport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7742">нумри Тал — пассапорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7742">numri tal-passaport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7743">НРУ Тал — пассапорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7743">Nru tal-passaport</span></span>

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7744">Идентификационный номер налога Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7744">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7745">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7745">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7746">Для национальных Мальтийский:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7746">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7747">семь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7747">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7748">Мальтийскийные страны и Мальтийский, не являющиеся субъектами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7748">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7749">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7749">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7750">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7750">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7751">Мальтийский Nationals: семь цифр и одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7751">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7752">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7752">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7753">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7753">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7754">Мальтийскийные страны и Мальтийский, не связанные с организациями: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7754">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7755">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7755">nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7756">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7756">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7757">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7757">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7758">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7758">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7759">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7759">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7760">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` ищет содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7760">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7761">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7761">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7762">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7762">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7763">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` ищет содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7763">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7796">Номер службы (BSN) для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7796">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7797">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7797">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7798">восемь девяти цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7798">eight-nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7799">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7799">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7800">восемь девяти цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7800">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7801">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7801">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7802">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7802">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7803">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7803">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7804">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7804">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7805">две три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7805">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7806">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7806">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7807">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7807">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7808">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7808">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7809">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7809">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7810">функция Func_netherlands_bsn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7810">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7811">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_netherlands_bsn;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7811">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7812">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7812">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7826">персунснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7826">persoonsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7827">соЦиаал — фискаал нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7827">sociaal-fiscaal nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7828">социальное — финансовый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7828">social-fiscal number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7829">софи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7829">sofi</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7832">униек идентитеитснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7832">uniek identiteitsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7833">уникальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7833">unique identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7834">уникальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7834">unique identity number</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7836">Номер водительского удостоверения для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7836">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7837">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7837">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7838">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7838">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7839">десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7839">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7840">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7840">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7841">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7841">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7842">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7842">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7843">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7843">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7844">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7844">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7845">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7845">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7846">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7846">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7847">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7847">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="6247fbea-ab80-4be5-8233-308b7c031401" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7975">Номер паспорта Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7975">Netherlands passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7976">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7976">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7977">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7977">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7978">девять букв или цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7978">nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7979">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7979">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7980">девять букв или цифр;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7980">nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7981">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7981">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7982">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7982">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7983">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7983">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7984">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7984">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7985">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7985">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7986">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7986">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7987">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7987">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7996">Идентификационный номер налога Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7996">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7997">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7997">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7998">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7998">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-7999">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-7999">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8000">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8000">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8001">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8001">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8002">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8002">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8003">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8003">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8004">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8004">nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8005">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8005">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8006">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8006">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8007">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8007">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8008">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8008">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8009">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8009">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8010">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8010">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8011">Функция  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8011">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8012">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8012">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8013">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8013">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8014">Функция  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8014">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8053">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8053">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8054">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8054">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8055">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8055">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8056">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8056">information governance</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8058">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8058">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8059">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8059">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8060">14-буквенно-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8060">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8061">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8061">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8062">14-буквенно-буквенно-символьный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8062">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8063">N или n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8063">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8064">L или l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8064">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8065">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8065">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8066">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8066">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8067">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8067">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8068">B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8068">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8069">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8069">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8070">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8070">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8071">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8071">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8072">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8072">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8073">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8073">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8074">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8074">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8075">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8075">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8076">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8076">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8077">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8077">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="4f320d9b-4972-41ae-b337-88d499bb1ade" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8082">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8082">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8083">веарде тафоеже налога на жетал</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8083">wearde tafoege tax getal</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8084">БТВ нûмер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8084">btw nûmer</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8086">Номер банковского счета Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8086">New Zealand bank account number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8087">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8087">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8088">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8088">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8089">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8089">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8090">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8090">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8091">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8091">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8092">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8092">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8093">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8093">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8094">шаблон с 14 до 16 цифр с необязательным разделителем</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8094">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8095">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8095">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8096">шаблон с 14 до 16 цифр с необязательным разделителем:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8096">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8097">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8097">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8098">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8098">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8099">от трех до четырех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8099">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8100">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8100">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8101">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8101">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8102">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8102">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8103">две до трех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8103">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8104">Параметры дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8104">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8105">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8105">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8106">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8106">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8107">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8107">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8108">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8108">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8109">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8109">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8110">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8110">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8111">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8111">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8112">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8112">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zFealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8120">Номер водительского удостоверения для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8120">New Zealand driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8121">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8121">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8122">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8122">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8123">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8123">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8124">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8124">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8125">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8125">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8126">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8126">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8127">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8127">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8128">8-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8128">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8129">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8129">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8130">8-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8130">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8131">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8131">two letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8132">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8132">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8133">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8133">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8134">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8134">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8135">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8135">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8136">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8136">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8137">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8137">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8138">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8138">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8139">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8139">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8140">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8140">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8145">драйвер Лик</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8145">driver lic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8146">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8146">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8147">лицензии на драйверы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8147">driver licences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8148">дриверслик</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8148">driverslic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8149">дриверслиценце</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8149">driverslicence</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8154">лицензии на драйверы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8154">drivers licences</span></span>
