## <a name="new-zealand-inland-revenue-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8207">Номер дохода по некоторому контакту для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8207">New Zealand inland revenue number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8208">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8208">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8209">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8209">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8210">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8210">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8211">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8211">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8212">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8212">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8213">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8213">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8214">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8214">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8215">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8215">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8216">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8216">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8217">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8217">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8218">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8218">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8219">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8219">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8220">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8220">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8221">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8221">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8222">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8222">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8223">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8223">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8224">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8224">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8225">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8225">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8226">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8226">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8227">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8227">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8228">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8228">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8229">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8229">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8230">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8230">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8231">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8231">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8232">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8232">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8233">ИРД но.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8233">ird no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8234">ИРД нет #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8234">ird no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8235">NZ ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8235">nz ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8236">Новая Зеландия ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8236">new zealand ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8237">номер ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8237">ird number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8238">номер дохода на землю</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8238">inland revenue number</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8239">Номер министерства здоровья Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8239">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8240">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8240">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8241">три буквы, пробел (необязательно) и четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8241">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8242">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8242">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8243">три буквы (без учета регистра), за исключением "I" и "O"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8243">three letters (not case sensitive) except 'I' and 'O'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8244">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8244">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8245">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8245">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8246">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8246">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8247">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8247">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8248">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8248">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8249">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8249">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8250">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8250">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8251">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_nz_terms;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8251">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8252">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8252">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8253">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8253">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8254">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8254">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8255">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8255">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
    <Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
       </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8256">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8256">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_nz_terms"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8257">Keyword_nz_terms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8257">Keyword_nz_terms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8258">нхи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8258">NHI</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8259">Новая Зеландия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8259">New Zealand</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8260">Здравоохранение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8260">Health</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8261">обращения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8261">treatment</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8262">Номер индекса национальной работоспособности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8262">National Health Index Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8263">номер Нхи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8263">nhi number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8264">Нхи но.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8264">nhi no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8265">нхи #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8265">NHI#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8266">Номер индекса национальной работоспособности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8266">National Health Index No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8267">Идентификатор индекса национальной работоспособности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8267">National Health Index Id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8268">Номер национальной работоспособности #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8268">National Health Index #</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-social-wlefare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8269">Номер социального влефареа Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8269">New Zealand social wlefare number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8270">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8270">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8271">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8271">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8272">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8272">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8273">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8273">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8274">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8274">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8275">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8275">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8276">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8276">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8277">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8277">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8278">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8278">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8279">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8279">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8280">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8280">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8281">Необязательный перенос</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8281">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8282">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8282">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8283">Необязательный перенос</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8283">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8284">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8284">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8285">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8285">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8286">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8286">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8287">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8287">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8288">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8288">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8289">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8289">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8290">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8290">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8291">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8291">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8292">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8292">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8293">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8293">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8294">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8294">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8295">социальные велфаре #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8295">social welfare #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8296">социальные велфаре #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8296">social welfare#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8297">социальное велфаре No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8297">social welfare No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8298">номер социального велфаре</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8298">social welfare number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8299">свн #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8299">swn#</span></span>

   
## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8300">Идентификационный номер Норвегии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8300">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8301">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8301">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8302">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8302">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8303">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8303">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8304">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8304">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8305">шесть цифр в формате ддммгг — Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8305">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8306">индивидуальный номер из трех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8306">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8307">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8307">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8308">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8308">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8309">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8309">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8310">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8310">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8311">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8311">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8312">функция Func_norway_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8312">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8313">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_norway_id_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8313">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8314">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8314">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8315">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8315">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8316">функция Func_norway_id_numbe находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8316">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8317">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8317">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8318">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8318">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_norway_id_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8319">Keyword_norway_id_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8319">Keyword_norway_id_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8320">Personal identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8320">Personal identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8321">Norwegian ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8321">Norwegian ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8322">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8322">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8323">Процедура</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8323">Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8324">персоннуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8324">Personnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8325">фøдселснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8325">Fødselsnummer</span></span>

   
## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8326">Идентификационный номер единой системы для различных целей Филиппины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8326">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8327">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8327">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8328">12 цифр, разделенных дефисами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8328">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8329">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8329">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8330">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8330">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8331">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8331">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8332">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8332">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8333">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8333">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8334">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8334">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8335">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8335">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8336">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8336">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8337">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8337">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8338">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8338">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8339">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8339">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8340">регулярное выражение Regex_philippines_unified_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8340">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8341">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_philippines_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8341">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8342">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8342">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8343">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8343">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8344">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8344">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8345">умид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8345">UMID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8346">Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8346">Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8347">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8347">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8348">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8348">Poland driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8349">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8349">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8350">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8350">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8351">14 цифр, содержащих 2 косых черты.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8351">14 digits containing 2 forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8352">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8352">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8353">14 цифр и 2 косых черт:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8353">14 digits and 2 forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8354">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8354">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8355">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8355">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8356">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8356">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8357">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8357">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8358">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8358">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8359">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8359">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8360">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8360">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8361">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8361">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8362">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8362">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8363">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8363">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8364">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8364">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Poland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="24d51f99-ee9e-4060-a077-cae58cab1ee4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8488">Идентификационная карточка Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8488">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8489">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8489">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8490">три буквы и шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8490">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8491">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8491">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8492">три буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8492">three letters (not case sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8493">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8493">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8494">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8494">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8495">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8495">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8496">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8496">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8497">функция Func_polish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8497">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8498">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8498">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8499">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8499">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8500">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8500">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8501">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8501">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8502">Довóд особисти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8502">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8503">Нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8503">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8504">Назва i нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8504">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8505">Назва i НР доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8505">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8507">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8507">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8508">Dow.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8508">dow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8509">совместим.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8509">os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8510">Национальный идентификатор Польша (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8510">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8511">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8511">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8512">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8512">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8513">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8513">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8514">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения, в формате ГГММДД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8514">6 digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8515">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8515">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8516">1 контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8516">1 check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8517">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8517">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8518">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8518">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8519">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8519">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8520">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8520">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8521">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8521">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8522">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_pesel_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8522">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8523">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8523">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8524">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8524">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8525">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8525">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8526">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8526">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8533">НР. PESEL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8533">nr.-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8534">НР — PESEL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8534">nr-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8535">Нумер идентификацижни</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8535">numer identyfikacyjny</span></span>

## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8538">Номер паспорта для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8538">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8539">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8539">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8540">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8540">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8541">две буквы и семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8541">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8542">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8542">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8543">Две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8543">Two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8544">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8544">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8545">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8545">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8546">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8546">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8547">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8547">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8548">функция Func_polish_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8548">The function Func_polish_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8549">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8549">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8550">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8550">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
</Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8551">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8551">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8552">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8552">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8553">Нумер пасзпорту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8553">Numer paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8554">НР.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8554">Nr.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8555">пасзпорту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8555">Paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8556">пасзпорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8556">Paszport</span></span>

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8557">Номер РЕГОНа Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8557">Poland REGON number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8558">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8558">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8559">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8559">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8560">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8560">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8561">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8561">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8562">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8562">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8563">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8563">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8564">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8564">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8565">девять цифр или номер из 14 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8565">nine digit or 14 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8566">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8566">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8567">девять цифр или 14 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8567">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8568">девять цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8568">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8569">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8569">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8570">дискрецион</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8570">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8571">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8571">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8572">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8572">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8573">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8573">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8574">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8574">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8575">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8575">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8576">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8576">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8577">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_polish_regon_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8577">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8578">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8578">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

```xml

        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8596">Идентификационный номер для таможенного учета Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8596">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8597">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8597">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8598">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8598">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8599">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8599">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8600">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8600">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8601">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8601">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8602">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8602">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8603">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8603">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8604">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8604">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8605">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8605">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8606">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8606">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8607">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8607">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8608">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8608">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8609">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8609">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8610">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8610">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8611">Функция  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8611">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8612">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8612">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8642">Номер карточки с префиксом "Португалия"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8642">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8643">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8643">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8644">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8644">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8645">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8645">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8646">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8646">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8647">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8647">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8648">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8648">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8649">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8649">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8650">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8650">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8651">регулярное выражение Regex_portugal_citizen_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8651">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8652">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_portugal_citizen_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8652">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8659">документо de идентификаçãо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8659">documento de identificação</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8660">идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8660">id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8661">Идентификация нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8661">identification no</span></span>

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8672">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8672">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8673">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8673">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8674">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8674">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8675">два образца — две буквы, за которыми следуют 5-8 цифр со специальными символами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8675">two patterns - two letters followed by 5-8 digits with special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8676">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8676">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8677">Pattern 1: две буквы, за которыми следует 5/6 со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8677">Pattern 1: Two letters followed by 5/6 with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8678">Две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8678">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8679">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8679">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8680">Пять или шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8680">Five or Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8681">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8681">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8682">Одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8682">One digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8683">Шаблон 2: одна буква, за которой следуют 6/8 цифры со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8683">Pattern 2: One letter followed by 6/8 digits with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8684">Одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8684">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8685">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8685">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8686">Шесть или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8686">Six or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8687">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8687">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8688">одна цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8688">One digit</span></span>

    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8689">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8689">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8690">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8690">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8691">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8691">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8692">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8692">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8693">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8693">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8694">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8694">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="977f1e5a-2c33-4bcc-b516-95bb275cff23" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8826">Номер паспорта для Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8826">Portugal passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8827">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8827">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8828">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8828">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8829">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8829">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8830">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8830">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8831">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8831">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8832">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8832">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8833">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8833">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8834">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8834">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8835">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8835">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8836">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8836">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8837">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8837">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8838">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8838">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8839">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8839">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8863">Идентификационный номер для налога на Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8863">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8864">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8864">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8865">девять цифр с необязательными пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8865">nine digits with optional spaces</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8866">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8866">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8867">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8867">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8868">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8868">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8869">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8869">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8870">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8870">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8871">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8871">3 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8872">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8872">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8873">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8873">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8874">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8874">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8875">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8875">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8876">Функция  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8876">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8877">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8877">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8878">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8878">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8879">Функция  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8879">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8904">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Румыния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8904">Romania driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8905">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8905">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8906">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8906">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8907">один символ, за которым следуют восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8907">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8908">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8908">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8909">один символ, за которым следуют восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8909">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8910">одна буква (без учета регистра) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8910">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8911">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8911">eight digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8912">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8912">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8913">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8913">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8914">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8914">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8915">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8915">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8916">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8916">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-8917">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-8917">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="b5511ace-2fd8-4ae4-b6fc-c7c6e4689e3c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-personal-numeric-code-cnp"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9045">Персональный числовой код Румыния (КНП)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9045">Romania personal numeric code (CNP)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9046">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9046">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9047">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9047">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9048">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9048">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9049">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9049">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9050">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9050">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9051">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9051">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9052">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9052">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9053">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9053">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9054">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9054">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9055">1 цифра из 1-9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9055">1 digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9056">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9056">6 digits representing date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9057">2 цифры, которые могут быть 01-52 или 99</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9057">2 digits which can be 01-52 or 99</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9058">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9058">4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9059">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9059">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9060">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9060">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9061">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9061">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9062">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9062">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9063">Функция  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9063">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9064">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9064">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9065">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9065">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9066">Функция  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9066">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Personal Numerical Code (CNP) -->
      <Entity id="eb5fa399-fe28-4c67-8188-d63a616ed89c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
