## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9117">Номер паспорта для Румыния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9117">Romania passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9118">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9118">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9119">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9119">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9120">восемь или девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9120">eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9121">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9121">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9122">восемь или девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9122">eight or nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9123">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9123">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9124">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9124">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9125">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9125">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9126">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9126">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9127">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9127">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9128">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9128">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
```

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9162">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9162">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9163">Регулярное выражение Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9163">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml

      <Entity id="76ec2f5d-cedb-48e1-8070-1998794af445" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9218">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9218">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9219">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9219">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9220">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9220">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9221">десять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9221">ten consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9222">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9222">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9223">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9223">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9224">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9224">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9225">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9225">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9226">регулярное выражение Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9226">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9227">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9227">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->

    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9233">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9233">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span></span> 

   
## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9234">Номер национальной идентификационной карточки для регистрации (NRIC), Сингапур</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9234">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9235">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9235">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9236">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9236">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9237">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9237">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9238">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9238">nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9239">буква "F", "G", "S" или "T" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9239">the letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9240">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9240">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9241">цифра алфавитной проверки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9241">an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9242">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9242">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9243">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9243">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9244">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9244">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9245">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9245">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9246">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9246">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9247">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_singapore_nric;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9247">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9248">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9248">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9249">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9249">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9250">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9250">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9251">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9251">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9262">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Словакия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9262">Slovakia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9263">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9263">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9264">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9264">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9265">один символ, за которым следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9265">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9266">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9266">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9267">один символ, за которым следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9267">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9268">одна буква (без учета регистра) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9268">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9269">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9269">seven digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9270">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9270">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9271">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9271">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9272">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9272">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9273">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9273">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9274">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9274">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9275">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9275">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="14240c22-b6de-4ce5-a90b-137f74252513" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-personal-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9401">Словакия персональный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9401">Slovakia personal number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9402">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9402">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9403">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9403">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9404">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9404">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9405">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9405">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9406">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9406">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9407">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9407">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9408">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9408">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9409">девять или десять цифр, содержащих необязательную обратную косую черту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9409">nine or ten digits containing optional backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9410">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9410">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9411">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9411">6 digits representing date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9412">Необязательная косая черта (/)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9412">optional slash (/)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9413">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9413">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9414">1 обязательная контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9414">1 optional check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9415">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9415">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9416">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9416">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9417">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9417">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9418">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9418">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9419">Функция  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9419">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9420">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9420">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9421">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9421">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9422">Функция  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9422">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Personal Number -->
      <Entity id="951c26b7-3b35-4f73-924b-15dd599cb9ab" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="slovakia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9469">Словакия — номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9469">Slovakia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9470">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9470">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9471">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9471">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9472">одна цифра или буква, за которой следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9472">one digit or letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9473">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9473">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9474">одна цифра или буква (без учета регистра), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9474">one digit or letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9475">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9475">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9476">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9476">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9477">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9477">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9478">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9478">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9479">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9479">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9480">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9480">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9499">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Словения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9499">Slovenia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9500">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9500">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9501">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9501">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9502">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9502">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9503">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9503">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9504">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9504">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9505">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9505">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9506">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9506">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9507">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9507">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9508">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9508">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9509">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9509">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9510">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9510">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5bc089a-f2ee-433d-a6b1-5c253051d6f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-unique-master-citizen-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9637">Словения уникальный номер хозяина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9637">Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9638">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9638">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9639">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9639">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9640">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9640">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9641">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9641">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9642">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9642">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9643">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9643">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9644">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9644">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9645">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9645">13 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9646">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9646">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9647">13 цифр в указанном шаблоне:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9647">13 digits in the specified pattern:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9648">семь цифр, которые соответствуют дате рождения (ДДММЛЛЛ), где "ЛЛЛ" соответствует последним трем цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9648">seven digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMLLL) where "LLL" corresponds to the last three digits of the birth year</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9649">две цифры, соответствующие области рождения "50"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9649">two digits that correspond to the area of birth "50"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9650">три цифры, которые соответствуют сочетанию пола и серийного номера для людей, которые приставили один и тот же день (000-499 для пола и 500-999 для розетки)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9650">three digits that correspond to a combination of gender and serial number for persons born on the same day (000-499 for male and 500-999 for female)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9651">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9651">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9652">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9652">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9653">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9653">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9654">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9654">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9655">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9655">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9656">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9656">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9657">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9657">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9658">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9658">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9659">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9659">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number -->
      <Entity id="68948b27-803d-41e4-adf1-13e05eb541bb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9687">Номер паспорта для Словения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9687">Slovenia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9688">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9688">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9689">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9689">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9690">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9690">two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9691">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9691">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9692">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9692">two letters followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9693">буква "P"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9693">the letter "P"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9694">одна прописная буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9694">one uppercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9695">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9695">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9696">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9696">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9697">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9697">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9698">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9698">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9699">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9699">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9700">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9700">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9701">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9701">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9702">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9702">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number_common"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9703">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9703">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9707">паспорты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9707">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9708">пасспортно</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9708">passportno</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9710">пасспортнумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9710">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9711">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9711">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9712">пасспортнумберс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9712">passportnumbers</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9716">потек велжавности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9716">potek veljavnosti</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9718">Datum рожства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9718">datum rojstva</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9720">šтевилке потних листов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9720">številke potnih listov</span></span>

## <a name="slovenia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9721">Идентификационный номер для налога на Словения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9721">Slovenia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9722">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9722">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9723">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9723">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9724">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9724">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9725">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9725">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9726">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9726">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9727">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9727">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9728">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9728">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9729">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9729">eight digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9730">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9730">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9731">одна цифра из 1-9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9731">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9732">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9732">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9733">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9733">one check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9734">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9734">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9735">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9735">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9736">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9736">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9737">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9737">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9738">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9738">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9739">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9739">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9740">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9740">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9741">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9741">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="e47b071e-c352-4d70-8241-8c215ad65505" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9752">налог без #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9752">tax no#</span></span>

## <a name="south-africa-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9765">Идентификационный номер Южно-Африканского Республика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9765">South Africa identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9766">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9766">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9767">13 цифр, которые могут содержать пробелы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9767">13 digits that may contain spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9768">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9768">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9769">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9769">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9770">шесть цифр в формате ГГММДД Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9770">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9771">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9771">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9772">Индикатор гражданства, состоящих из одной цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9772">a single-digit citizenship indicator</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9773">цифра "8" или "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9773">the digit "8" or "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9774">одна цифра контрольной суммы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9774">one digit which is a checksum digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9775">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9775">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9776">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9776">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9777">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9777">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9778">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9778">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9779">функция Func_south_africa_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9779">The function Func_south_africa_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9780">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_africa_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9780">A keyword from Keyword_south_africa_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9781">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9781">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Africa Identification Number -->
<Entity id="e2adf7cb-8ea6-4048-a2ed-d89eb65f2780" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_africa_identification_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_africa_identification_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9782">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9782">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_africa_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9783">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9783">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9784">Identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9784">Identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9785">ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9785">ID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9786">Процедура</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9786">Identification</span></span> 
   
## <a name="south-korea-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9787">Регистрационный номер резидентной Южной Кореи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9787">South Korea resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9788">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9788">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9789">13 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9789">13 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9790">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9790">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9791">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9791">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9792">шесть цифр в формате ГГММДД Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9792">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9793">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9793">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9794">одна цифра, определяемая столетием и пол</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9794">one digit determined by the century and gender</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9795">код региона рождения из четырех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9795">four-digit region-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9796">одна цифра, используемая для различения людей, для которых предыдущие числа идентичны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9796">one digit used to differentiate people for whom the preceding numbers are identical</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9797">контрольная цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9797">a check digit.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9798">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9798">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9799">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9799">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9800">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9800">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9801">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9801">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9802">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9802">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9803">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_korea_resident_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9803">A keyword from Keyword_south_korea_resident_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9804">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9804">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9805">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9805">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9806">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9806">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9807">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9807">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Korea Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="5b802e18-ba80-44c4-bc83-bf2ad36ae36a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9808">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9808">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_korea_resident_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9809">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9809">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9810">National ID card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9810">National ID card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9811">Citizen's Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9811">Citizen's Registration Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9812">Jumin deungnok beonho</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9812">Jumin deungnok beonho</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9813">ррн</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9813">RRN</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9814">주민등록번호</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9814">주민등록번호</span></span>

## <a name="spain-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9815">Номер водительского удостоверения для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9815">Spain driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9816">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9816">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9817">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9817">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9818">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9818">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9819">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9819">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9820">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9820">eight digits followed by one character:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9821">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9821">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9822">одна цифра или буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9822">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9823">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9823">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9824">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9824">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9825">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9825">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9826">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9826">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9827">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` или `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9827">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9828">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9828">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9829">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9829">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9830">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` или `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9830">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5a82922-b501-4f40-8868-341321146aa2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-dni"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9964">Испания, DNI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9964">Spain DNI</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9965">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9965">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9966">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9966">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9967">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9967">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9968">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9968">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9969">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9969">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9970">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9970">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9971">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9971">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9972">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9972">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9973">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9973">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9974">семь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9974">seven digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9975">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9975">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9976">Необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9976">An optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9977">один проверочный символ (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9977">one check letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9978">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9978">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9979">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9979">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9980">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9980">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9981">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9981">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9982">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` или `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9982">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9983">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9983">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9984">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9984">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-9985">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` или `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-9985">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

    
```xml
      <!-- Spain DNI -->
      <Entity id="8e6251b9-47b4-40e8-a42b-0f80876be192" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10009">Номер паспорта для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10009">Spain passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10010">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10010">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10011">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10011">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10012">сочетание букв и цифр из восьми или девяти символов без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10012">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10013">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10013">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10014">сочетание букв и цифр из восьми или девяти символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10014">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10015">две цифры или буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10015">two digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10016">одна цифра или буква (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10016">one digit or letter (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10017">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10017">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10018">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10018">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10019">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10019">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10020">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10020">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10021">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10021">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10022">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10022">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10023">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10023">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10032">пасспортнумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10032">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10033">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10033">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10034">пасспортнумберс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10034">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10035">номера паспортов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10035">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_spain_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10036">Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10036">Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10037">либрета пасапорте</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10037">libreta pasaporte</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10038">нúмеро пасапорте</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10038">número pasaporte</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10039">еспаñа пасапорте</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10039">españa pasaporte</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10040">нúмерос de пасапорте</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10040">números de pasaporte</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10041">нúмеро de пасапорте</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10041">número de pasaporte</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10042">нúмерос пасапорте</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10042">números pasaporte</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10043">пасапорте нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10043">pasaporte no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10044">Пассепорт n °</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10044">Passeport n°</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10047">пасапорте n °</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10047">pasaporte n°</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10048">Служба Passport, Испания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10048">spain passport</span></span>


## <a name="spain-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10049">Номер социального страхования (SSN) Испания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10049">Spain social security number (SSN)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10050">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в номер социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентный тип конфиденциальной информации и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10050">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10051">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10051">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10052">11–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10052">11-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10053">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10053">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10054">11-12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10054">11-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10055">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10055">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10056">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10056">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10057">семь и восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10057">seven to eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10058">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10058">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10059">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10059">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10060">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10060">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10061">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10061">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10062">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10062">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10063">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10063">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10064">функция Func_spanish_social_security_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10064">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10065">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10065">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Spain SSN -->
<Entity id="5df987c0-8eae-4bce-ace7-b316347f3070" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10066">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10066">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10067">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10067">None</span></span>

## <a name="spain-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10068">Налоговый идентификационный номер Испания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10068">Spain tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10069">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10069">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10070">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10070">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10071">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10071">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10072">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10072">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10073">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10073">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10074">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10074">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10075">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10075">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10076">семь или восемь цифр, а также одна или две буквы в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10076">seven or eight digits and one or two letters in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10077">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10077">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10078">Испанские пользователи с национальной идентификационной карточкой Испании Испания:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10078">Spanish Natural Persons with a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10079">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10079">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10080">одна прописная буква (с учетом регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10080">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10081">Нерезидентские Спаниардс без национальной идентификационной карточки Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10081">Non-resident Spaniards without a Spain National Identity Card</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10099">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10099">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10100">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10100">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10101">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` или `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10101">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10102">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10102">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10103">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10103">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10104">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` или `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10104">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="10f0d113-b0e1-47dc-872a-a4f45b9376a3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
