## <a name="sql-server-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10135">Строка подключения к SQL Server</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10135">SQL Server connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10136">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10136">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10137">Строка "идентификатор пользователя", "идентификатор пользователя", "UID" или "UserId", за которыми следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10137">The string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10138">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10138">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10139">строка "идентификатор пользователя", "идентификатор пользователя", "UID" или "UserId"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10139">the string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10140">Любая комбинация из 1-200 прописных или строчных букв, цифр, символов, специальных символов и пробелов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10140">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10141">строка "Password" или "pwd", где "pwd" не предшествует буква нижнего регистра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10141">the string "Password" or "pwd" where "pwd" is not preceded by a lowercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10142">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10142">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10143">любой символ, не являющийся знаком доллара ($), символ процента (%), символ "больше" (>), символ "@", "символ" (@), знак кавычек ("), точка с запятой (;), левая фигурная скобка ([) или левая квадратная скобка ({)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10143">any character that is not a dollar sign ($), percent symbol (%), greater than symbol (>), at symbol (@), quotation mark ("), semicolon (;), left brace([), or left bracket ({)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10144">Любая комбинация 7-128 символов, не отделяющая точку с запятой (;), косая черта (/) или кавычки (").</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10144">any combination of 7-128 characters that are not a semicolon (;), forward slash (/), or quotation mark (")</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10145">точка с запятой (;) или кавычки (")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10145">a semicolon (;) or quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10146">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10146">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10147">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10147">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10148">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10148">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10149">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10149">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10150">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10150">The regular expression CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10151">**Не** найдено ключевое слово из CEP_GlobalFilter.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10151">A keyword from CEP_GlobalFilter is **not** found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10152">Регулярное выражение CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder не **находит содержимое** , которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10152">The regular expression CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10153">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не **находит содержимое** , которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10153">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```sql
<!---SQL Server Connection String>
<Entity id="e76b6205-d3cb-46f2-bd63-c90153f2f97d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_GlobalFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10154">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10154">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_globalfilter"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10155">CEP_GlobalFilter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10155">CEP_GlobalFilter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10156">Некоторые пароли</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10156">some-password</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10157">сомепассворд</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10157">somepassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10158">секретпассворд</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10158">secretPassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10159">примером</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10159">sample</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_passwordplaceholder"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10160">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10160">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10161">(Технически, обратите внимание, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации определяет эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10161">(Note that technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10162">Пароль или pwd, за которым следует 0-2 пробелов, знак равенства (=), 0-2 пробелы и звездочка (\*)--или--</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10162">Password or pwd followed by 0-2 spaces, an equal sign (=), 0-2 spaces, and an asterisk (\*) --OR--</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10163">Пароль или pwd, а затем:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10163">Password or pwd followed by:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10164">Знак равенства (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10164">Equal sign (=)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10165">Символ "меньше" (<)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10165">Less than symbol (<)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10166">Любое сочетание 1-200 символов, которые являются буквами верхнего или нижнего регистра, цифрами, звездочкой (\*), дефисом (-), подчеркиванием (_) или символом пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10166">Any combination of 1-200 characters that are upper- or lowercase letters, digits, an asterisk (\*), hyphen (-), underline (_), or whitespace character</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10167">Символ "больше" (>)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10167">Greater than symbol (>)</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10181">Номер водительского удостоверения драйвера Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10181">Sweden driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10182">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10182">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10183">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10183">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10184">десять цифр, содержащие дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10184">ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10185">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10185">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10186">десять цифр, содержащих дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10186">ten digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10187">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10187">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10188">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10188">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10189">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10189">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10190">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10190">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10191">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10191">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10192">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10192">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10193">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10193">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10194">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10194">The regular expression  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10195">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10195">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="70088720-90dd-47f5-805e-5525f3567391" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10328">Национальный идентификатор, Швеция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10328">Sweden national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10329">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10329">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10330">десять или 12 цифр и необязательный разделитель</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10330">ten or 12 digits and an optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10331">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10331">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10332">десять или 12 цифр, а также необязательный разделитель:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10332">ten or 12 digits and an optional delimiter:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10333">две цифры (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10333">two digits (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10334">Шесть цифр в формате даты ГГММДД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10334">Six digits in date format YYMMDD</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10335">разделитель "-" или "+" (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10335">delimiter of "-" or "+" (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10336">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10336">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10337">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10337">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10338">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10338">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10339">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10339">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10340">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10340">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10341">Функция `Func_swedish_national_identifier` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10341">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10342">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10342">A keyword from `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10343">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10343">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10344">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10344">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10345">Функция `Func_swedish_national_identifier` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10345">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10346">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10346">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden National ID -->
    <Entity id="f69aaf40-79be-4fac-8f05-fd1910d272c8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10365">Номер паспорта Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10365">Sweden passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10366">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10366">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10367">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10367">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10368">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10368">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10369">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10369">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10370">восемь последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10370">eight consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10371">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10371">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10372">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10372">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10373">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10373">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10374">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10374">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10375">регулярное выражение Regex_sweden_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10375">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10376">выполняется одно из следующих условий:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10376">one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10377">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10377">a keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10378">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sweden_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10378">a keyword from Keyword_sweden_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Sweden Passport Number -->
<Entity id="ba4e7456-55a9-4d89-9140-c33673553526" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10409">Номер социального страхования для Швеции или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10409">Sweden social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10410">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10410">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10411">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10411">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10412">12 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10412">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10413">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10413">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10414">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10414">12 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10415">восемь цифр, которые соответствуют дате рождения (ГГГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10415">eight digits that correspond to the birth date (YYYYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10416">три цифры, которые соответствуют серийному номеру, где:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10416">three digits that correspond to a serial number where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10417">Последняя цифра в числовом номере указывает на пол, назначая нечетное число для пола и четное число для розетки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10417">the last digit in the serial number indicates gender by the assignment of an odd number for male and an even number for female</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10418">до 1990, назначение серийного номера соответствует району, в котором был выпущен номер, или (если он родился до 1947), где он был удален, в соответствии с налоговыми записями на 1 января 1947 с особым кодом (как правило, 9 в седьмой цифре) для иммигрантс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10418">up to 1990, the assignment of serial number corresponded to the county where the bearer of the number was born or (if born before 1947) where he/she had been living, according to tax records, on January 1, 1947, with a special code (usually 9 as the 7th digit) for immigrants</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10419">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10419">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10420">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10420">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10421">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10421">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10422">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10422">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10423">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10423">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10424">Функция  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10424">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10425">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10425">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10426">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10426">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10427">Функция  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10427">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10428">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10428">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10429">Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10429">Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10430">личный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10430">personal id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10431">identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10431">identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10432">личный идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10432">personal id no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10433">Идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10433">identity no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10434">Идентификация нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10434">identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10435">персональный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10435">personal identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10436">Идентификатор персоннуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10436">personnummer id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10437">Идентификатор персонлигт — нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10437">personligt id-nummer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10439">персоннуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10439">personnummer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10442">идентификатионснумрет #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10442">identifikationsnumret#</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10443">Идентификационный номер налога для Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10443">Sweden tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10444">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10444">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10445">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10445">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10446">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10446">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10447">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10447">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10448">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10448">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10449">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10449">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10450">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10450">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10451">десять цифр и символ в указанном шаблоне;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10451">ten digits and a symbol in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10452">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10452">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10453">десять цифр и символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10453">ten digits and a symbol:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10454">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10454">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10455">знак плюс или минус</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10455">a plus sign or minus sign</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10456">три цифры, которые делают идентификационный номер уникальным, где:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10456">three digits that make the identification number unique where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10457">для номеров, выпущенных до 1990, седьмой и восьмой цифрой определяют район рождения или пользователей, порожденных иностранным пользователем.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10457">for numbers issued before 1990, the seventh and eighth digit identify the county of birth or foreign-born people</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10458">цифра в девятой позиции указывает на пол, который нечетен для пола или даже для розетки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10458">the digit in the ninth position indicates gender by either odd for male or even for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10459">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10459">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10460">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10460">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10461">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10461">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10462">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10462">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10463">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10463">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10464">Функция  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10464">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10465">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10465">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10466">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10466">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10467">Функция  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10467">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="139acba0-a5bc-4fbb-876d-f7a493ae8a40" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10468">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10468">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10479">идентификационный номер налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10479">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10480">налог без #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10480">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10481">налог без</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10481">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10482">Налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10482">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10483">Регистрационный номер налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10483">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10484">такси #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10484">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10485">таксидно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10485">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10486">таксиднумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10486">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10487">таксно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10487">taxno#</span></span>

## <a name="swift-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10493">Код SWIFT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10493">SWIFT code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10494">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10494">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10495">четыре буквы, за которыми следует 5-31 букв или цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10495">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10496">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10496">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10497">четыре буквы, за которыми следует 5-31 букв или цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10497">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10498">код банка из четырех букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10498">four-letter bank code (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10499">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10499">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10500">4–28 букв или цифр (основной номер банковского счета, BBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10500">4-28 letters or digits (the Basic Bank Account Number (BBAN))</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10501">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10501">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10502">одна – три буквы или цифры (остаток от BBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10502">one to three letters or digits (remainder of the BBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10503">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10503">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10504">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10504">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10505">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10505">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10506">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10506">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10507">регулярное выражение Regex_swift находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10507">The regular expression Regex_swift finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10508">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_swift.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10508">A keyword from Keyword_swift is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="cb2ab58c-9cb8-4c81-baf8-a4e106791df4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_swift" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_swift" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="switzerland-ssn-ahv-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10545">Номер АХВа для Швейцарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10545">Switzerland SSN AHV number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10546">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10546">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10547">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10547">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10548">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10548">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10549">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10549">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10550">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10550">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10551">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10551">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10552">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10552">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10553">13 цифра, цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10553">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10554">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10554">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10555">13 цифра:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10555">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10556">три цифры — 756</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10556">three digits - 756</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10557">Необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10557">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10558">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10558">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10559">Необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10559">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10560">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10560">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10561">Необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10561">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10562">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10562">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10563">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10563">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10564">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10564">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10565">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10565">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10566">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10566">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10567">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10567">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10568">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10568">A keyword from Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10569">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10569">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10570">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10570">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Swiss SSN AHV Number -->
      <Entity id="277cfa4b-6eaa-4a1b-9492-099dec849971" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10589">Идентификация персоннелле ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10589">identification personnelle id</span></span>

## <a name="taiwan-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10591">Национальный идентификационный номер для Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10591">Taiwan national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10592">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10592">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10593">одна буква (на английском языке), за которой следуют девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10593">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10594">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10594">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10595">одна буква (на английском языке), за которой следуют девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10595">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10596">одна буква (на английском языке, без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10596">one letter (in English, not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10597">цифра "1" или "2"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10597">the digit "1" or "2"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10598">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10598">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10599">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10599">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10600">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10600">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10601">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10601">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10602">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10602">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10603">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10603">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10604">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwanese_national_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10604">A keyword from Keyword_taiwanese_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10605">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10605">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10606">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10606">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10607">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10607">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10608">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10608">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwanese National ID -->
<Entity id="4C7BFC34-8DD1-421D-8FB7-6C6182C2AF03" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwanese_national_id" />
      </Pattern>
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
         <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
       </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10609">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10609">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10610">Keyword_taiwan_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10610">Keyword_taiwan_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10611">身份證字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10611">身份證字號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10612">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10612">身份證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10613">身份證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10613">身份證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10614">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10614">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10615">身分證字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10615">身分證字號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10616">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10616">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10617">身分證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10617">身分證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10618">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10618">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10619">身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10619">身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10620">國民身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10620">國民身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10621">簽名</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10621">簽名</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10622">蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10622">蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10623">簽名或蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10623">簽名或蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10624">簽章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10624">簽章</span></span>   
   
## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10625">Номер паспорта для Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10625">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10626">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10626">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10627">номер биометрического паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10627">biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10628">номер биометрической службы Passport: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10628">non-biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10629">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10629">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10630">номер биометрического паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10630">biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10631">символ "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10631">the character "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10632">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10632">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10633">номер биометрической службы Passport:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10633">non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10634">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10634">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10635">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10635">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10636">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10636">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10637">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10637">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10638">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10638">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10639">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10639">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10640">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10640">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10641">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10641">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10643">ROC passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10643">ROC passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10644">Passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10644">Passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10645">Passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10645">Passport no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10646">Passport Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10646">Passport Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10647">Passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10647">Passport #</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10648">护照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10648">护照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10649">中華民國護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10649">中華民國護照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10650">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10650">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span></span>
   
## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10651">Номер сертификата резидента (ARC/TARC) для Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10651">Taiwan resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10652">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10652">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10653">десять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10653">ten letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10654">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10654">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10655">десять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10655">ten letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10656">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10656">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10657">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10657">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10658">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10658">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10659">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10659">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10660">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10660">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10661">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10661">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10662">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10662">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10663">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10663">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10664">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10664">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10665">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10665">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10669">Identification card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10669">Identification card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10670">Alien Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10670">Alien Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10671">ARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10671">ARC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10672">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10672">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10675">外僑居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10675">外僑居留證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10676">台灣地區居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10676">台灣地區居留證</span></span> 

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10677">Код идентификации для тайского заполнения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10677">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10678">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10678">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10679">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10679">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10680">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10680">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10681">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10681">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10682">Первая цифра не равна нулю или девять</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10682">first digit is not zero  or nine</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10683">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10683">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10684">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10684">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10685">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10685">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10686">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10686">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10687">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10687">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10688">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10688">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10689">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10689">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10690">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10690">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10691">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10691">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10695">Идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10695">Identification Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10696">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10696">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10697">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10697">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10698">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10698">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>

## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10700">Турецкий национальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10700">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10701">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10701">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10702">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10702">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10703">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10703">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10704">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10704">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10705">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10705">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10706">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10706">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10707">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10707">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10708">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10708">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10709">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10709">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10710">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Turkish_National_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10710">A keyword from Keyword_Turkish_National_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10711">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10711">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10712">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10712">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10713">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10713">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_turkish_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10714">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10714">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10715">TC Кимлик No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10715">TC Kimlik No</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10716">TC Кимлик нумарасı</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10716">TC Kimlik numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10717">Ватандаşлıк нумарасı</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10717">Vatandaşlık numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10718">Ватандаşлıк нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10718">Vatandaşlık no</span></span>

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10719">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10719">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10720">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10720">driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10721">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10721">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10722">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10722">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10723">Сочетание 18 букв и цифр в указанном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10723">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10724">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10724">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10725">18 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10725">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10726">пять букв (без учета регистра) или цифра 9 вместо буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10726">five letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10727">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10727">one digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10728">пять цифр в формате даты ММДДИ для даты рождения (седьмой символ увеличивается на 50, если драйвер — гнездо, то есть 51 – 62, а не с 01 – 12)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10728">five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth (7th character is incremented by 50 if driver is female, i.e. 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10729">две буквы (без учета регистра) или цифра "9" вместо буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10729">two letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10730">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10730">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10731">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10731">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10732">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10732">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10733">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10733">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10734">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10734">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10735">функция Func_uk_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10735">The function Func_uk_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10736">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_drivers_license;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10736">A keyword from Keyword_uk_drivers_license is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10737">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10737">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10746">трициклес</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10746">tricycles</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10747">моторциклес</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10747">motorcycles</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10748">photocard licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10748">photocard licence</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10751">licence holders</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10751">licence holders</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10752">driving licences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10752">driving licences</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10753">driving licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10753">driving licence</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10754">dual control car</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10754">dual control car</span></span> 
   
## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10755">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10755">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10756">номер рулона електорал</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10756">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10757">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10757">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10758">две буквы, за которыми следуют 1-4 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10758">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10759">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10759">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10760">две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют 1-4 номера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10760">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10761">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10761">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10762">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10762">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10763">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10763">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10764">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10764">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10765">регулярное выражение Regex_uk_electoral находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10765">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10766">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_electoral.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10766">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10767">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10767">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_electoral"></a><span data-ttu-id="d0bfb-10768">Keyword_uk_electoral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d0bfb-10768">Keyword_uk_electoral</span></span>
